ISainsbury itsatsa indzawo yaBoots, Superdrug kanye naDebenhams ngetitolo tekutilungisa letitfungelwe letiphatfwa ngulabo labagulako.
Njengencenye yekukhutsata imakethe yebuhlakani yaseBrithani lengemakhulu lamane emali yetigidzi tetinkhulungwane, leyakhula ngesikhatsi lizinga lekunakekelwa kwebantfu lihle, ema-kiosos abukeka lamakhulu atawucala ku- 11 wetitolo eveni lonkhe futsi atawuchubeka akhule kute afinyelele etitolo letinyenti ngemnyaka lolandzelako nangabe loku kuyahamba.
Kufakwa kwetintfo letitfolakalako kulokwekutilungisa sekwenta kutsi ema-supermarket akhone kusebentisa kahle emashelufa awo kute agcine tintfo letifana nema-TV, ema-microwave kanye nemishini yasetindlini.
Sainsbury utsi loku kutakwenta kube kabili kukhula kwekuhlengwa kwemikhicito kute kube ngemikhicito le-3000, kufaka ekhatsi imikhicito lefana ne Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye na Dr. PawPaw kwekucala ngca.
Luhla lwemikhicito lekhona njenganyalo lecala nge LOreal, Maybelline kanye ne Burts Bees nayo itawutfola indzawo lenkhulu ngendzawo leyakhiwe ngemikhicito lefana nalena letfolakala etitolo letifana ne Boots.
Lesitolo siphindze savula luhla lwato lwetitolo letitsengisa tintfo tekugcobisa, ngako-ke lemikhicito yabo leminyenti itawuba ngulena lelungele bantfu labangadli kudla kwe tilwane - intfo leyakhula ibalulekile kubantfu labasha.
Ngetulu kwaloko, iFragrance Shop, lokungumtsengisi wetinongo, itawucala kuhweba ngetitolo letimbili eSainsbury, lekucala lelisungulwe e-Croydon, eningizimu yeLondon kuleliviki leliphelile, bese kutsi leliya lelisedvute livule e-Selly Oak, e-Birmingham, ngasekupheleni kwalomnyaka.
Kutsenga ngekusebentisa i-inthanethi kanye nekutsenga kudla lokuncane lokutfolakala etitolo, kusho kutsi emasuphamakethe kufanele ente lokunyenti kute akhange bantfu kutsi bavakashele lapho.
Mike Coupe, umphatsi lomkhulu weSainsbury, utsi letitolo titawuchubeka tifanane netitolo letitsengisa kudla lokunyenti njengobe letitolo letitsengisa kudla lokunyenti titama kulwa netitolo letititsengisa kudla lokunyenti njengaloku lokwentiwa bo-Aldi na-Lidl.
