Peter Jones uvele ngemuva kwekuhlubuka kwaHolly Willoughby kulesivumelwano lesingu £11 million.
Peter Jones washiya iDragons Den ngekuhlanya ngemuva kwekuhlubuka kwe-TV Holly Willoughby ngekushiya licebo lakhe lekuphila lelimisha lelingana tigidzi letingu £11 kute anake kakhulu umsebenti wakhe lomusha we-Marks and Spencer kanye ne-ITV.
Willoughby akanaso sikhatsi sekuphatsa timphahla tasendlini kanye netintfo letitsite.
Lelibhizinisi lalabobantfu labatsandzanako belifana ne-Goop brand laGwyneth Paltrow.
Lomengameli we-This Morning, loneminyaka lengu-37, wasebentisa i-Instagram yakhe kute amemetele kutsi uyahamba.
Holly Willoughby wacasula Petes Jones, umlingisi we Dragons' Den, ngekutihocobisa kwakhe kwekugcina, kusuka ebhizinisini lemphilo yabo leyayimzuzisa - kute anake kakhulu kuniketa kwakhe umsebenti lomkhulu we Marks & Spencer kanye ne ITV.
Imithombo itsi Jones bekangakhululekile ngesikhatsi le-TV lengenhla ivuma ngesikhatsi sekuhlangana lokucindzetelako ngaLesibili ehhovisi lakhe lelibhizimisi lelikhulu eMarlow, Buckinghamshire, kutsi kutsengiswa kwakhe lokusha - lokululeka ku-£1.5 million - kusho kutsi akasasenaso sikhatsi lesenele sekutimisela nge-truly, lokungumkhicito wabo wekusebenta ekhaya kanye netintfo letisetjentiswa ekhaya.
Lolokwenta kutsi kube yintfo lephindze yentiwe kutsi ibonakale njenge Goop, leyatiwa ngu Gwyneth Paltrow, futsi leyenta kutsi kube yintfo lephindze yenta kutsi Willoughby abe ngumuntfu lomkhulu ngemali lengemarandi latigidzi letilishumi nakunye.
Ngesikhatsi Willoughby, loneminyaka lengu-37, asebentisa i-Instagram akhangisa ngekutsi ushiye i-Truly, Jones wasuka eBritain aya kulelinye lalamakhaya akhe ebusika.
Umtfombo lotsite utsi: "Kucinisa, ngiko lokuyintfo lemcoka kakhulu kuHolly".
Bekukhomba kutsi bekutawuba likusasa lakhe lelisedvute, bekutawumenta kutsi akhone kuhlala iminyaka leminyenti.
Sincumo sakhe sekuyekela lomsebenti samangalisa bonkhe lebebahlanganyele kuwo.
Kute umuntfu lobekakholelwa kutsi loku bekwenteka ngaLesibili, ngobe besekusondzele sikhatsi sekusakateka.
Kunesitolo lesinetitja letigcwele e-Marlow's Head Office letihlelelwe kutsengiswa.
Labadzala belibandla beva buhlungu lobukhulu ngekushona kwaLobekangunkhanyenti wa-This Morning, lokwaholela ekutseni inkampani yakhe ibhajwe tigidzi temarandi ngenca yekutsatsa imali lenkhulu ekwakhiweni kwetintfo letitsite, kusukela emaluphini kanye nemabhandlela kuye kulokwekwembatsa kanye netintfo tasendlini, kanye nekubambezeleka lokukhulu kwekusungula.
Loku kungaphindze kusho kuphela kwebuhlobo lobunetikhatsi letinyenti.
Make webantfwana labatsatfu, Willoughby nendvodza yakhe Dan Baldwin bebabambisene kakhulu na Jones nemkakhe Tara Capp iminyaka lelishumi.
Willoughby wasungula iTruly naCapp nga-2016, futsi Jones, 52, wajoyina njengasosihlalo ngaMashi.
Laba lababili bebahamba ndzawonye, kantsi Jones unenhlanganyelo lengu-40% enkampanini leyakha ema-TV lacondziswe nguBaldwin.
Willoughby utawuba ngumkhonti weM&S futsi utawuvala Ant McPartlin njengemngcwabo we-ITV lotsi I'm A Celebrity.
Umuntfu losondzelene naJones ubike kutsi ebusuku kungeke sikhone kukhuluma ngaloludzaba.
