Kutamatama Kwemhlaba Kanye NeTitsunami E-Indonesia Kubulala Bantfu Labanyenti
Kwatsi ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba eLombok, sibonelo, tinhlangano tangaphandle letingekho ngaphasi kwahulumende tatjelwa kutsi atidzingeki.
Nanobe bantfu baseLombok labangetulu kwa-10% balahlekelwe tindzawo tekuhlala, kute simemetelo savelonkhe senhlekelele lesenteke, lokungumgomo lobalulekile kute kufinyelele lusito lwemave emhlaba.
Kweswela kutsi emaveni lamanyenti, bavele bavele bachaza kutsi abakaceli lusito lwemave emhlaba, ngako-ke loku kuyinsayeya", kwasho Ms Sumbung.
Njengobe i-Save the Children ilungiselela kuhamba kuya ePalu, akukabonakali kutsi ngabe tikhulu tangaphandle titawufika yini.
Umkhulumeli wesikhungo setenhlekelele, Mr. Sutopo, utsi tikhulu tase-Indonesia tibukisisa lesimo sasePalu kute tibone kutsi ngabe tikhungo tangaphandle tivumelekile yini kutsi tihlanganyele ekunikeni lusito.
Njengobe i-Indonesia ichubeka itfola kutamatama kwemhlaba, solo ayikakulungeli kubukana nekuhlupheka kwemvelo.
Nanobe kwakhiwa tikhungo tekuvikela ema-tsunami e-Aceh, akukavami kutsi kubekhona letintfo letivamile kulolubandze loluselugwadvule.
Kwehluleka kwecwayisa nge-tsunami ePalu, ngisho nobe bekusengakabi nekucwayisa, kungenteka kube yimbangela yekushona kwebantfu.
Etimeni letikahle, kuhamba kuleto tichingi letinyenti tase-Indonesia kumatima.
Tintfo letibangelwa tinhlekelele temvelo tenta luhlelo lwekuhambisa tintfo lube lukhuni kakhulu.
Sibhedlela lesikhukhulako lesiseLombok lesinakekela labo labahlukunyetiwe nguletintsaba sesitfunyelwa ePalu, kepha kutawutsatsa lokungenani emalanga lamatsatfu kutsi sifike kulendzawo lapho kwenteke khona letintsaba.
Umengameli Joko Widodo wenta kutsi kulungiswe takhiwonchanti tase-Indonesia letilimele kube yincenye yemkhankhaso wakhe wekukhetsela, futsi usebentise imali yakhe ekwakheni imigwaco kanye nemasitimela.
Kodvwa kweswelakala kwetimali sekubekele hulumende waMengameli Jokowi litfuba lekubalekela kukhetfwa kwakhe kutsi abe nguNdvunankhulu.
Lomunye umcindzeteli lobuswa ngulesimo sekungevani lokunemandla lokusachubeka khona e-Indonesia, lapho khona emalunga lamanyenti ema-Muslim emukele indlela lecinile yekukholwa.
Bangetulu kwe-1 000 bantfu labafa futsi emashumi etinkhulungwane ayabaleka lapho abehlala khona ngesikhatsi ema-Muslim nemaKhristu alwa etitaladini, asebentisa imimese, imicibisholo kanye naletinye tikhali.
