Bantfu labafa ngenca ye-tsunami e-Indonesia banyuke baba ngu-832
Bantfu labashone kuletitfukutfuku temhlaba kanye nasetitsaminini e-Indonesia sebafike ku-832, kusho i-National Disaster Management Agency ngeLisontfo ekuseni.
Bantfu labanyenti babikwa kutsi babambeke etingodvweni tetakhiwo letigugile ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-7.5 ngeSikali lokwenteka ngaLesihlanu, lokwabangela emagagasi langemamitha lasiphohlongo ngebudze, kusho Sutopo Purwo, sikhulumi salenkampani etinkhomfeni tebetindzaba.
Lelidolobha lelibitwa ngekutsi yiPalu, lelinebantfu labangetulu kwa-380 000, ligcwele tindvonga tetakhiwo letibhidlikile.
Emaphoyisa abambe indvodza leneminyaka lengu-32, ngekusolwa kwebugebengu ngemuva kwekutsi umfati ashayeke wafa.
Kuphenya ngekubhubha kwebantfu kwentiwe ngemuva kwekutsi sidvumbu semfati satfolwe eBirkenhead, Merseyside, ekuseni.
Umfati loneminyaka lengu-44 watfolakala asesemgwacweni iGrayson Mews, John Street, ngensimbi ya-7:55 ekuseni, anetimbobo letimbalwa, kantsi indvodza leneminyaka lengu-32 iboshelwe licala lekubulala.
Emaphoyisa acela bantfu labakuleligumbi kutsi bavule emehlo.
Luphiko lolusebaleni lolubitwa ngekutsi yi-Detective Inspector Brian O'Hagan lutsi: "Luphenyo lusetincenyeni tekucala kodvwa ngicela bonkhe labatawube basendzaweni yaseJohn Street eBirkenhead labatawube babonile nobe bevile lokutsite lokungabahluphi kutsi basitjele".
Ngiphindze ngicele bonkhe bantfu, ikakhulukati bashayeli bematekisi, kutsi babe bayabukela nobe yini kulabomabonakudze, kutsi babonane natsi ngobe kungenteka babe nalokutsite lokungaba lusito ekuphenyeni kwetfu.
Sikhulumi semaphoyisa sicinisekise kutsi lomake lokwatfolwa sidvumbu sakhe ngumuntfu wasendzaweni wase Birkenhead futsi watfolakala asesakhiweni.
Lamuhla kusihlwa, labangani bakhe labacinisekako kutsi bayamati lomfati, bafikile kulendzawo kute bamtjele kutsi utfolakale kuphi.
I-FBI isasebenta ngephasi kweluphenyo lwaleliphoyisa, lelisatimisele kutjela tihlobo talona lofile.
Umshayeli wetekisi lohlala eGrayson Mews usandza kubuya ekhaya lakhe, kodvwa emaphoyisa atjelwa kutsi kute umuntfu longena noma longena kulesigodvo.
