Liphoyisa livile umuntfu atjela lomunye kutsi lendzawo seyivele ibekelwe tigameko letibuhlungu.
Lomunye make wavela kulendzawo akhala.
Uhlale atsi, "Loku kubi kakhulu".
Ngetikhatsi telibhi elilanga lelishumi nambili emini, imoto yemaphoyisa lamabili beyime emgceni kanye nalenye lebeyime ngaphandle.
Emaphoyisa lamanyenti abuka lelibhilidi.
