Kodvwa bantfu baseCromwell bachaza leseluleko saMnu. Crick ngekutsi "sibuli" futsi "sifuna kubhala kabusha umlandvo".
John Goldsmith, losihlalo we Cromwell Society, watsi: "Kute indlela yekuphepha kulelicala lelikhona nyalo lekutsi kucekelwe phansi titfombe, kutsi titfombe ta Oliver Cromwell ngaphandle kwe sigodlo sase Westminster tibe yinhloso.
I-Iconoclasm yemphi yemhlaba yemaNgisi ayizange icondziswe nobe yentiwe ngu Cromwell.
Kungenteka kutsi titukulwane taCromwell letiliphutsa betitawubulawa ngenca yaloko lokwentiwa ngubabe wato, Thomas, eminyakeni leyendlulile.
Kumelelwa kwa Cromwell lokumangalisako kwaSir William Hamo Thorneycroft, kungubufakazi bemibono yelikhulu lesi-19 kanye nencenye yemlandvo wesibalo lesentiwa kutsi bantfu labanyenti basamtsandza.
Umnumzane Goldsmith watjela Sunday Telegraph kutsi: "Cromwell bekatsatfwa ngulabanyenti, mhlawumbe kakhulu ngeminyaka yabo-19 kunaloku lokungulamuhla, njengemvikeli wePhalamende nakunetiphatsimandla tangaphandle, esimeni sakhe vele bekungumuntfu wasebukhosini.
Lokutsi ngabe loku bekungumfanekiso lowenabile yini, kusolo kungumbono wemphikiswano lechubekako wemlandvo.
Lokwatiwako kutsi lemphi lesemkhatsini welikhulu lelishumi nesikhombisa leminyaka yacala kwakha indlela yesive lesilandzelako, futsi Cromwell bekungumuntfu lobekatati kahle kutsi yini leyenta lemphi ihluke.
Kuphumelela kwakhe njengeMvikeli weNkhosi kufanele kutsi kugcwaliswe ngekugubha umkhosi.
