Bangetulu kwetigidzi letimashumi lamabili bantfu labakubonile kwetfulwa kwelicala laBrett Kavanaugh.
Bangetulu kwetigidzi letimashumi lamabili bantfu lababone inkhulumo yemgcibelo lebeyiphume ngeLesine leyayentiwa ngummeli lophakeme kakhulu, Brett Kavanaugh kanye nemfati labamsola ngekutsi wente budlova bekusebenta ngetemacasi ngemnyaka wa 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, kumabonakudze lasitfupha.
Kwanyalo, kusuke sekungekho lutfo loluhle lolwentiwe, kusuke sekukhona tikhulumi letihlelekile letitoshumayela ngalokungahleleki lokwenteke ngaLesihlanu: Sivumelwano lesasentiwe nguSekela Mengameli wase-Arizona Jeff Flake, lesenta kutsi i-FBI ikhulume ngelicala lelimanga lelimanga lelakhokhe liviki lonkhe.
Ford watjela likomidi leSenate Judiciary kutsi lomfati unekuciniseka lokukhulu kutsi Kavanaugh wamdlwengula ngesikhatsi adakiwe futsi wetama nekumgcobisa timphahla takhe ngesikhatsi semcimbi wesikolwa.
Kavanaugh, ngekucophelela lokukhulu, utsi uciniseke ngalokuphelele kutsi loko akuzange kwenteke.
Kungenteka kutsi ngetulu kwa 20.4 million yebantfu labatibonile letitfombe, Nielsen lasebente ngabo ngaLesihlanu.
Le nkampani yabala lababukele ku CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne MSNBC.
Tikhungo letibukela lomsebenti atizange tibe khona ngekushesha, kufaka ekhatsi i-PBS, i-C-SPAN kanye ne-Fox Business Network.
Dan Nielsen abevame kuba nenkinga yekubalwa kwebantfu labambukelako ehhovisini lakhe.
Kute sikubeke engcondvweni, loko kungaba linani lelibukelwa ngulabantfu labanyenti njengasemdlalweni welibhola letinyawo nobe emcimbini wemklomelo wemakinati.
I-Fox News Channel, leyaba nembono webabukeli labahle kakhulu ngekukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh, beyikhetsiwe kuleyo nkundla ngekubukela tigidzi letingu-5,69 ngesikhatsi sekubanjwa kwelicala ngemini, kusho Nielsen.
I-ABC beyingesekela ngalabantfu labalinganiselwa kutigidzi letingu-3.26
I-CBS inebantfu labatigidzi letingu-3.1, i-NBC inebantfu labatigidzi letingu-2.94, i-MSNBC inebantfu labatigidzi letingu-2.89 bese-ke i-CNN inebantfu labatigidzi letingu-2.52, kusho i-Nielsen.
Kubantfu labangazange balibone lelicala, kodvwa kwatfutfuka.
Flake bekungumuntfu lobalulekile kumdlalo wangaLesihlanu.
Ngemuva kwekutsi likomidi lelicembu lelinguMengameli wembuso likhiphe inkhulumo lephikisako kutsi litawusekela Kavanaugh, wabanjwa ngema-CNN nema-CBS ngeLesihlanu ekuseni ngesikhatsi bamshaya bamkhahlameta ngesikhatsi etama kungena efemini lekhwela lifti lelibangise ekutseni likomidi leNkantolo yeMtsetfo.
Wema ngetinyawo imizuzu lembalwa ngesikhatsi ahlatjwa, lokuchutjwa ku CNN.
"Ngimi lobuke wena", kwasho lomake.
Ucabanga kutsi ukhuluma liciniso yini kulelive?
Watjelwa kutsi, "Unemandla lapho khona emakhosikati angakhoni kusita".
Flake watsi lihhovisi lakhe likhiphe lesitatimende futsi watsi, ngaphambi kwekutsi kuvalwe letindzawo tekukhuphukela, kukhona lokunyenti lokudzinga kutsi akutjele likomidi.
I-TV lekhashane kanye nemsakato wemakhebuli konkhe kwahamba kwaphela ema-awa lambalwa ngemuva kwaloko, ngesikhatsi Likomidi Letemtsetfo litawukhetsa kutsi liletse i- Kavanaugh kutsi imiswe ngemalunga eSigungu Savelonkhe kutsi ayovota.
Kodvwa Flake utsi utawenta njalo kuphela nangabe i-FBI isafuna kuhlolisisa lelicala lelimelene naloyo muntfu evikini lelilandzelako, njengobe loku kucelwe licembu lelincane lema-Democrats.
Flake ucinisekiswe yincenye yencociswano yakhe nalomunye umngani wakhe, Sisebenti seSigungu Lesikhulu Chris Coons.
Ngemuva kwekukhuluma naCoons kanye nalamanye ema senethi, Flake wenta sincumo sakhe.
Kukhetfwa kwaFlake kwaba nemandla, ngobe bekusolo kucace bha kutsi emaRepublican bekangeke abe nelivi lekuvuma Kavanaugh ngaphandle kwekutsi kube khona luphenyo.
Mengameli Trump uvule luphenyo lwe-FBI mayelana netinsolo letiseceleni kwa Kavanaugh.
