Tikhatsi letinyenti, emacembu lafuna inkhululeko bekamemeta "kungakhohlwa, kungatsetselelwa" abhekene netitfunywa telicembu letibukene nekumemeta, "kuphila kweSpain".
Bantfu labalishumi nakune batfola imitsi yekulashwa kwetilondza letincane labatitfole kulombhikisho, kubika tindzaba takulesigodzi.
Tikhungutsalo tihlala tikhulu kulendzawo lebeyifuna inkhululeko, ngemuva kwenyanga ye-Okthoba 1 lebeyibitwa ngekutsi yi-referendum lebeyingekho emtsetfweni yi-Madrid kepha yagujwa ngema-Catalan labencike ekususweni kwe-Catalan.
Labavoti bakhetsa kuba ngema-Independents, nanobe linani leliphansi lebakhetsiwe, labo labebaphikisana nekuhlukana ne-Independent, bebangekho, futsi linyenti labo bebangafuni kuvota.
Ngekusho kwabomandla beCatalan, bantfu labangaba likhulu balimala emnyakeni lophelile ngemuva kwekutsi emaphoyisa etame kumisa kuvota etindzaweni tekuvikela tigebengu kulo lonkhe lelive, ngekungevani lokukhulu.
Emacembu laphakamisa inkhululeko abekadze acambele ebusuku ngaLesihlanu kute acedzele umbhikisho wekusekela emaphoyisa avelonkhe.
Imibhikisho yachubeka kepha baphocelelwa kutsi batsatse letinye tindlela.
Narcis Termes, 68, sisebenti se-electrician lesasihambele umbhikisho webahlaseli belubandlululo kanye nemkakhe, utsi akasaphefumuli ngelikusasa lelikhona le-Catalonia.
"Ngemnyaka lophelile, sibe nesikhatsi lesihle.
Ngibone batali bami bakhala ngenca yekukhetsa, kodvwa nyalo sesibambekile", kwasho yena.
Ngisho nobe bebangakazuzi kahle elukhetfweni lwavelonkhe ngaDecember, emacembu emibuso lefuna inkhululeko yaseCatalan alwela kugcina umfutfo wawo lomnyaka nanobe baholi bawo labanyenti labatiwako, labasekudzingisweni nobe labasemajele balindzele kubekwa kwabo licala, ngendzima labayidla ekuhleleni luhlolo lwelukhetfo lolulandzelako kanye nekumenyetelwa kwenkhululeko.
Joan Puig, longumakhenikha loneminyaka lengu-42 budzala, lowafaka i-video yekuphikisa ngemakhalekhikhini wakhe kute asekele emaphoyisa, utsi lemphi yacala ngekuhlanganyela kwebaholi bemacembu omabili.
"Manje sekuyingoti kakhulu", kwasho yena.
Ngalesikhatsi kungalolusuku, Oriol Junqueras, munye walabasiphohlongo labatsatfu labatsatfu labagwetjwe ejele lase Catalonia kusukela ngemnyaka lophelile, umemetele kutsi utawuvota elukhetfweni lwePhalamende yaseYurophu emnyakeni lotako.
