Emakhulu ebantfu abulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba, tsunami, kanye nelinani lelisetulu lebantfu labashona
Bantfu labangu-384 babulawa, labanyenti bashaywa, kwatsi emagagasi lamakhulu agadla elugwini, ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami kugadla esihlengeni sase-Indonesia, eSulawesi, kusho tiphatsimandla ngeMgcibelo.
Emakhulu ebantfu abutsanela kugubha lelilanga lelikhulu elugwini lwelidolobha iPalu ngaLesihlanu ngesikhatsi ligagasi lelingemamitha lasitfupha budze (18 feet) lihlasela lolwandle entsambama, libulala bantfu labanyenti futsi licekela phansi konkhe lokudlulako.
Ngemuva kwaloko, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwaba ngu-7.5.
Ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemvula kuhlasela, bantfu bebasolo benta imisebenti yabo lebeseceleni kwelwandle futsi abazange basuke lapho kute batfole imphilo, kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, lomelele i-BNPB, ngesikhatsi ahlangana nebantfu eJakarta.
Litsunami alizange lifike lingedvwa, lahlwitsela timoto, tihlahla, tindlu, labhidlita konkhe lokwakungemanti, kusho Nugroho, ngekwengeta kutsi le tsunami yahambela elwandle ngekushesha lokungaba ngu 800 kph (497 mph) ngaphambi kwekushaya emnceleni.
Labanye bantfu bagcwala tihlahla kute babalekele le-tsunami, futsi batsi baphila.
Bantfu labangaba ngu-16,700 batfunyelwe etindzaweni tekukhosela letingu-24 ePalu.
Titfombe tetinkhanyeti letikhishwe yi-BNPB tikhombisa tindlu letinyenti kanye netitolo letibhidlitwe, emabhuloho labhidlikile kanye nemasikhamu lagcwatjwe ngemanti.
Tintfo letibuhlungu talandzela letinye letenteka kuleLesihlanu.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla kwacala endzaweni lehlala bantfu labatigidzi letingu 2,4.
I-Bureau for the Study and Application of Technology (BPPT) itsi emandleni etintsaba letinkhulu letenteka ngaLesihlanu, emandla ato akhona aphindvwe ka-200 kunalawo lavela ngesikhatsi kubhadalwa ibhomu ye-athomu eHiroshima ngeMphi Yelive Yesibili.
Lokubekwa kwalelidolobha, lelisemkhatsini wemigudvu lemidze, kwenta sikhala semanti kutsi sikhule sibe sikhulu.
Kubhujiswa kwalesakhiwo kwachazwa ngekutsi "kubi" futsi kwachaza kutsi tinkhulungwane temakhaya, tibhedlela, tindzawo tekutsengiselana kanye nemahhotela kubhujisiwe.
Imitimba yalabantfu yatfolwa ibambeke ngaphansi kwetindumbu tetakhiwo letishayekile, kwatsiwa, kwengeta kutsi kunebantfu labangu 540 labasindze baphindze balimala kantsi labangu 29 bayanyamalala.
Nugroho utsi kubulala kanye nekubhujiswa bekungaba kukhulu endzaweni letiganga leti khilomitha letingu 300 (190 miles) ngasenyakatfo kwePalu, indzawo lebitwa ngekutsi yiDonggala, lelisedvute nalendzawo lekwaba khona kutamatama kwemhlaba.
"Kute kuchumana lokuhlelekile ngaphandle kwemniningwane lovela ku Donggala", kusho Nugroho.
Kunebantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000 labahlala lapho, kusho i-Red Cross esitatimendeni, yengeta ngekutsi emalunga abo kanye nemavolontiya aya endzaweni lechwalile.
