John Edward: Kusebentisa lulwimi kubaluleke kakhulu kubantfu bemhlaba wonkhe
Tikolwa taseScotland tihlale tinemlandvo wekuhlonishwa etikwaloko lokufundzako, lokuchubeke nga-2018 ngekuphumelela lokumangalisako etihlolweni, lokuchubekiswe ngekwengeta kwemfundzi ngamunye kanye nekuphumelela lokukhulu emidlalweni, etintfweni tebuciko, emculweni kanye nasetintfweni letiyimphumelelo.
Ngabafundzi labangetulu kwa-30 000 labafundza etikolweni taseScotland, tikolo leti, letimele nguMkhandlu WetiSikolo Letimele (Scottish Council of Independent Schools) tiyasebenta kamatima kuletsa tinsita letikahle kubafundzi nakubatali.
Tikolo letimele tifuna kufundzisa bafundzi kutsi batfole imfundvo lephakeme, imisebenti labayitsandzako, kanye nemisebenti yabo njengebahlali bemhlaba.
Njengemkhakha wetemfundvo longakhela uphindze usebentise luhlelo lwebukhona besikolo ngendlela lefanele, sibona kutsi tilwimi tesimanje tichubeka nekutfutfuka njengetifundvo letifunwako naletifunwako etikolweni letinyenti.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, uyakuva ngemcondvo wakhe.
Nawukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko kumfikela enhlitiyweni".
Loku kusikhumbuta ngalokucacile kutsi singete satsembela esiNgisini kuphela nasitfutfukisa budlelwane kanye nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Emaphuzu lasemkhatsini waletiluhlaka teluhlolo lolwentiwe kulomnyaka, sibona kutsi lulwimi luphakeme kakhulu etikolweni letifundzisako.
Emaphesenti langu-68 ebantfwana labafundza tilwimi letinye batfola ema-A plus.
Lemininingwane, lebutfwe etikolweni letingu 74 letingumalunga e-SCIS, ikhombisa kutsi bafundzi labangu 72% batfola emaBanga laKhulu ngeSiswati, kantsi labangu 72% bafundza siJalimane, 69% bafundza siFulentji, 63% bafundza siSpanishi, baphindze batfola emaBanga laKhulu.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa taseScotland tiyasekela kukhuluma tilwimi te-afrika njengelwati lolubalulekile lolutawufuneka kubantfwana nebantfwana labaseminyakeni yekutfomba esikhatsini lesitako.
Nyalo, tilwimi, njengekufundza ngekukhetsa, tifundvwa ngendlela lefanako netintfo letitfolwa ngema-STEM (sayensi, tebucwephesha, bungcweti netibalo) etikolweni tangomuhla kanye nakuletinye tindzawo.
Luhlolo lolwentiwe yi-UK Department of Employment and Skills nga-2014 lwatfola kutsi ngetizatfu letilishumi nesikhombisa tekutsi kungani bacashi kufanele bachubeke nekusebenta kute bagcwalise tikhala temisebenti, emaphesenti la-17 aloku bekungukungabi nemakhono ekusebentisa lulwimi.
Ngaloko, likhono lekulwati lulwimi liyakhutsatwa kwentela kucecesha bantfu labasha ngemisebenti yabo yesikhatsi lesitako.
Ngetisebenti letinyenti letifuna lwati lwetilwimi, lamakhono abalulekile emhlabeni lowendlulele.
Kunobe ngumuphi umsebenti umuntfu langakhetsa kuwwenta, uma ngabe sebafundze lulwimi lwesibili batawujabulela tinzuzo tekuba nalolwati imphilo yabo yonkhe.
Kucoca nebantfu labavela kulamanye emave kungenta kutsi umuntfu lokwati kukhuluma ngetilwimi letinyenti abe nemandla lamakhulu ekuncintisana nalabanye.
Ngekusho kwelucwaningo lwe-YouGov lolwentiwe kubantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4 000 base-UK nga-2013, emaphesenti langu-75 abo akakhulumi tilwimi letinye ngalokwenele kute bacoce, kantsi lulwimi lwesiFulentji lulona kuphela lolukhulunywa ngema-digit lamabili ngalokuphindvwe kabili, lokwenta emaphesenti langu-15.
Kungako-ke kubalulekile kutsi sisebentise imali ekufundziseni bantfwana betfu tilwimi lamuhla.
Kuba nelwati lwetilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati tilwimi letisemnotfweni, kutawuniketa bantfwana ematfuba lamanyenti ekutfola umsebenti lonetimphawu letinhle.
eScotland, sikolwa ngasinye sitawuhlela tifundvo ngelulwimi lolusebentako.
Letinye tikolwa titakwenta lokukhulu ngetilwimi tesimanje, letinye titawusebentisa tilwimi letitawufundziswa eminyakeni leminyenti letako, njengaloku i-Mandarin nobe iJapane.
Nobe ngabe yini umntfwana wakho layitsandzako, kutawuba netinhlobo letehlukene telulwimi letingafundvwa esikolweni lesifundzisa ngelulwimi, lesinabofundzisi labaceceshiwe.
Sikolwa saseScotland lesitimele sihlose kuniketa imphilo yekufundza letawulungiselela bantfwana kanye nekubahlomisa ngemakhono ladzingekako kute baphumelele, noma ngabe yini letawenteka esikhatsini lesitako.
Akukafaneli kutsi sikuphike kutsi lamuhla, esimeni sebhizinisi yemhlaba wonkhe, lulwimi lutawuchubeka lube yintfo lebalulekile ekuchazeni likusasa lalelive, ngako-ke kufanele kuvetwe kufundza.
Ecinisweni, tilwimi tesimanje kufanele tibhekwe "njengelwati lwekukhulumisana nalamanye emave".
