Luhlelo lwe-Trump lwe-West Virginia Public Meeting, i-YouTube Channel
Mengameli Donald Trump ucala umhlangano wakhe wetinkhankala tepolitiki lamuhla ebusuku eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
Lona ngumhlangano wekucala waTrump lotawubanjwa ngemaviki lasihlanu lalandzelako, kufaka ekhatsi tindzawo letijabulisako letifaka ekhatsi iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngekucinisekisa kutsi lokuvota kuyahlehliswa kute akhone kukhetsa umengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme, Trump ufuna kwakha livoti lakhe lelimsekelako elukhetfweni lolutako lwekhatsi ne-Riphabliki ingase ilahlekelwe kulawula i-Congress uma lokuvota kwenteka ngeNgongoni.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi semhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia kulobusuku, futsi ungasibuka njani ku-internet?
Umhlangano waTrump eWheeling, eWest Virginia, uhlelelwe sikhatsi lesingu 7 ebusuku, ET kusihlwa, ngeMgcibelo, 29 Septemba 2018.
Ungatitsatsela umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia ku-inthanethi ngekutsi ubukele i-YouTube.
Kukhona kutsi Trump utawucoca kulenchubo yelicala leNkhulu kuleliviki lebukene nelicala leNkhululeko Brett Kavanaugh, lelisondzele kakhulu ngemuva kwekumangalelwa ngekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicansi futsi nekubiketela kutsi livoti leSeneti litawubekwa licala liviki linye ngesikhatsi i-FBI iphenya ngaloludzaba.
Kodvwa-ke, injongo lenkhulu yaloluhlelo lwekuhlangana ngukutsi kusite i-Republican Party kutsi itfole emandla ekubamba lomkhankhaso lomatima ngelukhetfo lwaNovemba.
