"Kugadza umhlangano weTinkantolo Kubaluleke kakhulu ku-ajenda yakhe kute umengameli ahambe aye etigodzini letinyenti ngendlela lekungakhoneka ngayo njengobe sisengcebeni yekukhankasa", kusho sikhulumi saTrump lesingafuni kubitwa ngemagama satjela Reuters.
Kulomhlangano lobekelwe eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, kulindzeleke kutsi kube nemicimbi levela e-Ohio nasePennsylvania kanye nasePittsburgh, kusho i-West Virginia Metro News.
