Ryder Cup 2018: I-USA ibambe lichaza ngekubeketela ekudzingisweni ngeLisontfo
Ngemuva kwemahlandla lamatsatfu lanemacembu lahlukene, umcimbi welicembu linye ngeMgcibelo ntsambama nguloko lokungenteka kutsi kudzingeka kutsi kwentiwe kulomdlalo welicembu lelimhlophe.
Umdlalo wekugucula umfutfo ngumdlalo wemcondvo lokhishwe etintfweni letitsatfwa ngulabadlali, futsi kute lokunye lokwendlula lomdlalo.
Basho kutsi lamanti ashona lapho.
"Bekungu 6 lebebahola, manje sebangu 4, ngicabanga kutsi loku kuyintfo lembi kakhulu", kwasho Jordan Spieth abuka emuva ngalolusuku.
I-Europe inelitsemba lekutsi inemaphuzu lamane ngemidlalo lelishumi nakubili.
Kodvwa licembu laseMelika, njengobe Spieth asho, litiva linemandla lamancane futsi linetintfo letinyenti letingaba yinshisekelo, ngaphandle kwa Spieth na Justin Thomas labadlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe futsi labatsatsa lamatsatfu kumane.
Spieth udlale ngendlela lemangalisako kusuka kulelitje kuye kuleligceke futsi uhola ngekwenta sibonelo.
Umsindvo wekukhuluma lokukhulu wacala kukhula ngesikhatsi sekusondzela sikhatsi, kwatsi ngekusebentisa liphutfumisa lelibalulekile lelakha umchudzelwano ngesikhatsi yena naThomas balahlekelwa ngemadvodza lamabili.
Kukhokha kwakhe lijazi lelishaya kubo ku 15 kwaphendvuleka ngekumemeta lokufanako, kumemeta lokwatjela kutsi bekaciniseka kutsi iMelika angeke ize ihlulwe.
"Kufanele utame kamatima futsi ukhatsateke ngemdlalo wakho", kwasho Spieth.
Bonkhe labadlala indzima sebaphumile.
18 leyayidzinga kuphawulwa.
Umdlali munye lonemaphuzu lamanyenti kuna Spieth na Thomas kulamalanga lamabili lendlulile ngu Francesco Molinari na Tommy Fleetwood, indzaba lengeke iphikiswe ye Ryder Cup.
Imibhangqwana leyehlukile kepha lenhle yaseYurophu nguletine kuya kulabane futsi ingenta ngaphandle kwemaphutsa.
"Moliwood" ngiwo kuphela emacembu lalingeke ashaya bogey ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, kepha nawo bekangafaki bogey ngeMgcibelo ekuseni, ngeLesihlanu ntsambama kanye ne-back nine ngeLesihlanu ekuseni.
Kujabha kwabo, nendlela emandla abo labekabonakala ngayo nakungena nakuphuma kulesicumbi lesiphitsitelako, kwabenta baciniseka kutsi ngibo labadlali lebebatawushaywa ngeLisontfo, futsi kute lomunye umdlali lowatiwako kunabo Fleetwood nobe Molinari labatawuvala umnyango wekutsi iYurophu incobe nakushona lilanga ku-Le Golf National.
Kuncono kakhulu kutsi tibekwe ngaletindlela letehlukene ngesikhatsi sinye.
Nanobe kunjalo, kusesenesikhatsi kutsi sikhulume ngekuncoba kweYurophu.
Bubba Watson kanye na Webb Simpson bacedze Sergio Garcia, i-fourball hero yasekuseni, ngesikhatsi bamdvweba na-Alex Noren.
Ligama linye lelingasilo licala linye kanye nemabili laphindvwe kabili kuletinyanga letiyimfica tekugcina, kufana nekutsi ukhiphe umgodzi longeke uphumelele lotawukhashelwa ngulabadlali beligiligiligi leSpanish neSweden.
Noma kunjalo, ngeLisontfo kute longakusita uphume kulobo bunzima.
I-Fourball ne-Foursome iyincenye lenhle yekuhlola indlela lababili labaphetse ngayo, kutsi basiniketa tiphi teluleko, kutsi basiniketa tiphi teluleko nekutsi bangawagucula njani emasu abo ngekushesha.
Kwanyalo, emacembu aseYurophu adlala kancono futsi ahamba phambili ngalokwenele ngelilanga lekugcina, kepha le-foursome ikhombisa kutsi emacembu aseMelika anesibindzi sekungenela lomncintiswano, ngisho noma labanye, ikakhulu eMelika, bakungabata.
Emacembu aseYurophu ayahamba ngemalengiso nga-10-6 ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup
I-Europe itawuphumelela kulelolanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekuphumelela emdlalweni we-fourball kanye ne-foursome ngaMgcibelo ngemiphumela lengu-10 kuya ku-6 ngembi kwe-United States.
Tommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari bachuba ngemaphuzu lamabili, ngemuva kwekuncoba Tiger Woods, lobekufanele alwe kute kube ngunyalo ku-Le Golf National ngemaphuzu lamane.
Thomas Bjorn waseYurophu, lobekafuna kugcina umchele wakhe labengakawutfoli ku Hazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, wahlupha licembu laseMelika lelakwenta liphutsa lelingakahleleki ekuseni, lelakwenta kwaba ngu 3-1.
Ema-Amerika aniketa imphumelelo lenkhulu kubantfu labane, ancoba imidlalo lemibili, kepha akakhoni kwehlisa kubandlululwa kwawo.
Licembu laJim Furyk lalidzinga emaphuzu lasiphohlongo kulishumi nakubili lelidlalwe ngeLisontfo kute lihlale lincobile.
Fleetwood waba wekucala eYurophu kuwina emaphuzu lamane ngekulandzelana, yena kanye na Molinari, labesebabitwa ngekutsi "Molliwood" ngemuva kwemaphetselo lamahle, baba ngulababili kuphela labawina emaphuzu lamane ekucala kwemidlalo yabo lemine emlandvweni we-Ryder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekuncoba bo-Woods naPatrick Reed ngemabhola lamane, sebacinile kuncoba bo-Woods labamnyama kanye ne-Bryson Dechambeau, umSA wekucala, ngemabhola lamane.
Woods, lowatihlanganisa naye ngemidlalo yakhe lemibili ngaMgcibelo, bekavame kuvelela kepha bekaphulelwe ngumdlalo wakhe wemashumi lamabili nakunye emahlandla lamabili nemfica.
Justin Rose, lofike walala nge fourball ekuseni, wabuya wahlangana na Henrik Stenson nge foursome futsi wahlulwa 2 na-1 ngu Dustin Johnson na Brooks Koepka - labatsatfu labadlala indzawo yekucala emhlabeni.
IYurophu ayizange ifinyelele lapho ngekwayo ngisho nangesikhatsi semoya lomuhle, eningizimu-ntshonalanga yeParis.
Emacembu lamatsatfu lahlwile, Jordan Spieth na Justin Thomas, babeke lizinga lelisetulu eMelika ngemaphuzu lamabili ngalomgcibelo.
Baphindze bancuma kuhlulwa nguJon Rahm na Ian Poulter base Spain ngemadvolo lamane baphindze bancuma kuhlulwa nguPoulter na Rory McIlroy ngemadvolo lamane nalamatsatfu ngemuva kwekulahlekelwa ngemigodzi lemibili yekucala.
Kwenteke kabili kuphela emlandvweni we-Ryder Cup kutsi licembu lebuyele emuva ngemaphuzu lamane kungena umdlalo munye, nanobe njengemcashi lophetse licembu laFuryk belisidzinge emaphuzu layingcwaba kute liwine umchele.
Kodvwa ngemuva kwekubekwa njengalesibili kulelinani emalangeni lamabili, kuhlasela kwabo lokwentiwe ngeLisontfo kubukeka shengatsi kutawubangemukelela.
INorth Korea itsi 'akukafaneli' kutsi ivele nje icedzele tikhali tayo ngaphandle kwekwetsembana
NgeMgcibelo, Ndvunankhulu wase North Korea utjele iUN mayelana netigwebo letitfutfukisako letijulisa kungetsembakali kwabo eMelika nekutsi angeke kwenteke kutsi live lelinguNuclear lilahle tikhali talo te-nuclear ngesizatfu saloko.
Ri Yong Ho, lowatjela umhlangano wemnyaka we-World Nuclear Forum, watsi i-North Korea itsatse "tinyatselo letibonakalako letibonisa kutsandza kwenta lokuhle" kulomnyaka lophelile, njengekuyekela kuhlola emathuluzi enuzi nemabhomu, kukhipha tikhungo tekuhlola emathuluzi enuzi, kanye nekutetsembisa kutsi angeke ihlakulele tikhali tenuclear nobe bucwepheshe baleto.
"Noko, asikwati kuphendvula lokukahle lokuvela eMelika", kwasho yena.
"Kute kwetsemba iMelika kute litsemba ekuvikeleni sive setfu futsi esimeni lesinjalo akukafaneli kutsi sivele ngekutibamba kwetfu".
Ngalesikhatsi Ri abuyisa lokunye kwekukhonona kwase North Korea mayelana nekuphikiswa kwe Washington ngendlela "lencane" yekucedza i-denuclearization lapho khona iNorth Korea itawuhlushwa ngekutsatsa tinyatselo kancane kancane, inkhulumo lebalulekile yentiwa kutsi ayisho kutsi bayayekela ngalokuphelele njengoba kwenta Pyongyang esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri ukhuluma ngesimemetelo lesentiwe ngu Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump emhlanganweni wekucala wabomengameli baseMelika nebakhulu baseNyakatfo Korea lowabanjwa eSingapore ngaJuni 12, lapho khona Kim wacinisa kutsi utawuletsa "kuphelelwa ngemandla ngwenya" eNingizimu Korea, kantsi Trump yena wacinisa ngekucinisekisa kuphepha kweNyakatfo Korea.
I-North Korea beyifuna kutsi kuphele lemphi ye-Korean yemnyaka wa-1950 kuya ku-53, kepha i-United States itsi Pyongyang kumele icale ngekucedza tikhali te-nuclear.
I-Washington nayo ivimbe yonkhe imibiko lefuna kutsi kucitfwe lokuciniswa lokucinile kwebugebengu lobubhekiswe eNyakatfo yeKorea.
"I-United States ibambelela kakhulu ekutseni "kucala ngekukhipha tikhali te-nuclear" futsi yenta umfutfo ngekuniketa imitsetfo levimbela kufinyelela kumgomo wabo ngekucindzetelwa, futsi ingete yavuma "kucedza imphi", kusho Ri.
"Litsemba lekutsi kungabekwa licala lelimatima embikwetfu, yintfo lekhohliswe bantfu labangati lutfo ngatsi.
Inkinga nje kutsi lokuchubeka kwentiwa kucinisa kungetsembani kwetfu".
Ri akazange akhulume ngemhlangano wesibili emkhatsini wa Kim na Trump lowavetwa ngemholi wase United States eNhlanganweni Wetive Emhlaba ekucaleni kwalelisontfo.
Lencenye yalesitfombe iphindze yaveta kutsi bekubambe umhlangano wekugcina emkhatsini waKim kanye nemholi waseNingizimu Korea, Moon Jae-in, ngetinyanga letisihlanu letengcile, kwatsi leminye imicimbi yaletsi: "Uma ngabe iNingizimu Korea ngiyo lenetinkinga kuloku kwehlulwa kwekuhlanganiswa kwethrafikhi, hhayi iMelika, loku kwehlulwa kwekuhlanganiswa kwethrafikhi kwe-peninsula yaseKorea bekungeke kucale".
Nanobe kunjalo, inkhulumo yaRi yehluke kakhulu kunalena lebeyentiwa ngemnyaka lophelile, lapho khona etfula inkhulumo yakhe emhlanganweni we UN lowatiwa ngekutsi yi UN General Assembly, lapho akhuluma khona ngekutsi kubekwa kwetikhali temphi tase North Korea emhlabatsini wase United States bekungeke kuphele ngemuva kwekutsi "Mengameli Loyingoti" Trump abite Kim "indvodza yemarokhethi" leyayenta umsebenti wekubulala.
Kulomnyaka, emhlanganweni we-UN, Trump, lowatsi ngemnyaka lowengcile wetama "kubhubhisa" i-North Korea, utfokotele Kim ngesibindzi sakhe sekutsatsa sinyatselo sekukhipha tikhali, kepha lomsebenti lomnyenti usetawuchubeka futsi nekugcizelela kumele kuhlale kunetinyatselo kuze i-North Korea ikhulule tikhali tayo.
NgeLesibili, Trump watsi kute sikhatsi lesincunywe ngulesikhatsi, "Nangabe kungatsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu - akunandzaba", kusho yena.
I-China kanye ne-Russia, ticabanga kutsi Sigungu Lesiphetse se-UN kufanele sijezise i-Pyongyang ngaletinyatselo letibhalwe phansi.
Nanobe kunjalo, iNdvuna yeMbuso yaseMelika, Mike Pompeo, itjele Likomidi Letekuphepha le-UN kutsi: "Kucinisekiswa kwetigwebo teMkhandlu Wetekuphepha kumele kuchubeke ngekucinisa futsi kungaphumeleli kuze kube ngulapho sesati kutsi kucedvwa kwenyukliya kuphelele, sekuphelele futsi kucinisekisiwe".
Umkhandlu wetekuphepha wamukela ngalokuphelele kutsi kunconywe tinyatselo letitsite te-N. Korea kusukela nga-2006 kwentela kucedza kucedza imali lekhishwe yi-Pyongyang kute ivikele tinhlelo tayo tetentakusa kanye netentfo letisezingeni lelisetulu.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi emacaleni e-UN General Assembly wase utsi ngemuva kwaloko utawuvakashela i-Pyongyang futsi ngenyanga letako kute alungiselele umhlangano wesibili.
Pompeo uvakashele eNyakatfo Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kepha luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina alukaphumeleli kahle.
Wasuka ePyongyang ngaJulayi watsi kukhona lokwentekile, kepha bekungukutsi ngekhatsi kwemahora lambalwa bebangena eNyakatfo Korea, kutsi bekafuna "kufana nelicembu letigelekece".
I-North Korea yetsembisa emhlanganweni ne Moon kulenyanga kutsi itawuvala tindzawo tayo tekusebentisa tikhali kanye netintfo tayo te-nuclear uma i-United States itsatsa "sinyatselo lesifanele".
Watsi Kim wamtjela kutsi ente "lokutsite" lokuhambisana naloku bekakufuna. Loku bekusicinisekiso sekuphepha lesatsenjiswa nguTrump eSingapore kanye nekuhamba endleleni yekusungula budlelwane lobuhle ne Washington.
Bafundzi ba-Harvard bafundza inkhulumo lemayelana nekuphumula lokwanele
Kucala luhlelo lolusha eHarvard University lomnyaka lotsi bonkhe bafundzi babhudze kakhulu, kwentela kulwa nemkhuba wekutifundzela webulili lowenta bantfu bagcwale caffeine.
Lesinye sati satfola kutsi bafundzi basemanyuvesi laphakeme kunawo onkhe emhlabeni, bavame kuba bete lwati lolubanti lwekutsi bangativikela njani.
Charles Czeisler, longuphrofesa wetekwelapha lofundzela kufundza ngekulala eHarvard Medical School kanye nasetindzaweni letisebenta kuto tibhedlela iBrigham and Women's, waklama indlela yekufundzisa, lakholelwa kutsi ngiyo yekucala lesebenta eMelika.
Wagcugcutelwa kutsi acale lesifundvo ngemuva kwekwetfula inkhulumo lemayelana nemiphumela yekungalali kahle.
'Ekugcineni, kwefika intfombatana kimi yatsi: "Kungani ngisolo ngingakabikelwa ngemnyaka wami wekugcina?"
"Lentfombatana yatsi kute umuntfu lowake wangitjela ngekubaluleka kwekulala - loku kwangimangalisa kakhulu", kusho yena kuThe Telegraph.
Kulesifundvo, lesetfulwe kwekucala kulomnyaka, kufundzisa bafundzi kutsi indlela lenhle yekulala ingasita njani emphumelelweni yabo yetemfundvo, kutemidlalo kanye nasemphilweni yabo.
Paul Barreira, longuphrofesa wekusebenta kwengcondvo eHarvard Medical School kanye nemcondzisi lomkhulu wetemphilo enyuvesi, utsi leyonyuvesi yakhetsa kufundzisa bantfu labangafuni kulala ngemuva kwekutfola kutsi labafundzi bebangakhoni kulala kahle.
Lenkhulumo lefundvwa ngeli-awa linye, ifaka ekhatsi luchungechunge lwemisebenti lelandzelanako.
Kuloko, kunesitfombe selibhodlela lapho khona bafundzi bakhona bacondze etitjeni tabo letibanti telikhofi, emashadini, emabhulukwe, kanye netincwadzi kute batfole inchazelo lemayelana nemtselela we caffeine kanye nezibani, nekutsi imiphumela yetemidlalo itsintseka njani ngekungalali kahle, kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala ngalokwetayelekile.
Kulesinye sigaba, labalingani bafundziswa kutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungeta bungoti bekuhlaselwa sifo senhlitiyo, kushaywa sifo senhlitiyo, kucindzeteleka kwemcondvo kanye nemdlavuza.
Lelisu lekukhomba indzawo lesekhatsi ekhampasi, leline-icon lebonwako, bese ikhutsata bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemikhuba yabo ya onkhe malanga.
'Besati kutsi loku ngeke kugucule indlela umfundzi lacabanga ngayo ngekushesha.
Kodvwa siyaciniseka kutsi banalo lilungelo lekwati - njengobe nawe unalo lekwati ngemiphumela yekubhema,' kusho Prof. Czeisler.
Utsi lisiko lekutikhukhumeta ngekulala ebusuku lisekhona, kodvwa bucwepheshe besimanje kanye nekucindzeteleka kwebafundzi kwenta kungalali kahle kube yinkinga lenkhulu.
Kucinisekisa kutsi utfola sikhatsi lesenele sekulala, kufanele kube 'sikhali sakho semfihlo' sekulwa nekucindzeteleka, kudzinwa nekukhatsateka, utsi - ngisho nekugwema kukhuluphala, ngobe kungalali kahle kwenta ingcondvo yakho isebentise indlela yekushintja indlala, lokwenta kutsi uhlale ulambile.
Raymond So, umfundzi waseCalifornia loneminyaka lengu-19 lowati ngekusebenta kwemitsi kanye netintfo letiphilako lowasita Profesa Czeisler ekutfutfukiseni lenchubo, wafundza yinye yetinkhundla takhe emnyakeni wakhe wekucala eHarvard.
Utsi lemfundvo yamvula emehlo akhe futsi yamkhutsata kutsi ahlele lemfundvo emakilasini lasemphumalanga.
Kwesibili, ufuna bonkhe bafundzi labatfola ticu te-UCSF bafundziswe kutsi bafundze imfundvo lefananako ngaphambi kwekutsi baye kuletinye tikhungo.
Profesa Czeisler ucebisa kutsi bafundzi bafanele bacabange ngekubeka li-alamu lekulala, li-alamu lekuvuka, kanye nekunaka imiphumela lebukene nekukhanyisa lokuluhlata sasibhakabhaka lokukhishwa ngemabhokisi kanye netibani te-LED, lokungasusa indlela yakho yesigcilikisha lesimise kuloko lokumele kwentiwe, bese kubangela tinkinga tekulala.
I-Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Igoli lelishaya phansi libutfo lemphi lemphi laGerrard
Kwatsi nje, emaRangers abona buhlungu bekuphuma kwelilanga ngesikhatsi Dolly Meng asho indlela yekubuyela emuva kwa Steven Gerrard, lokwabangela kutsi bahlukane ngemalengiso 1-0 e-Livingston.
Liqembu le Ibrox belifuna kutfola kuncoba kwekucala kusukela kuncoba kwabo nga 4-1 ngaFebhuwari eSt Johnstone, kepha Gary Holt usandza kuniketa Gerrard kuncoba kwakhe kwesibili emidlalweni yakhe lelishumi nesiphohlongo, kwamshiya ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo ngemuva kwe Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.
I-Menga ihlasela sekusele emaminitsi lasikhombisa kutsi kube nesisindvo sekucala futsi ema-Rangers lanengcondvo yekungacabangi asacala kubukana nekucina.
I-Rangers seyihlehliselwe kulesitfupha, Livingston sewuphetse kulesitsatfu, ngemuva kweligalo le-Hibernian.
Kantsi futsi kungenteka kube nenkinga lenkhulu ebaleni le Ranger ngemuva kwekutsi umgadzi Calum Spence afakwe esibhedlela ngenca yekulimala enhloko ngemuva kwekugwazwa yintfo lebeyichamuka khashane.
Gerrard wenta tingucuko letisiphohlongo ecenjini lelakhokha iAyr kuya kumigamu ye Betfred Cup.
Esikhundleni saloko, Holt uyahamba naleli Livi 11 lelicondze libuye lelilungelo lelicondze iHearts ngeliviki leliphelile futsi utawujabula kakhulu nakangakhona kuhlaba umxhwele titsa takhe.
