Umlingisi we-Game of Thrones Kit Harington usola kutsi emadvodza ayintfo lengcolile
Kit Harington watiwa kakhulu ngekuhlaba inkemba yakhe njengemlingisi wa Jon Snow ku-HBO Game of Thrones, inoveli yemaphupho leyayinebudlova.
Kodvwa lomdlali, loneminyaka lengu-31 budzala, uphikisana nalombono we-macho, utsi letilwimi letisetjentiswa titsiwa "tindzima temadvodza" tibangela kutsi bantfwana labaseminyakeni yekutfomba bative shengatsi kufanele babe nemandla kute bahlonishwe.
Kukhuluma ne The Sunday Times Culture, Kit watsi ukholelwa kutsi 'kunetintfo letingekho kahle' futsi wabuta kutsi ngabe kunjani kulawula bulukhuni lobukhulu lobutsite nge #MeToo.
Kit, losandza kushada nemlingisi wakhe kuGame of Thrones, Rose Leslie, naye lokungu-31, utsi utiva 'anemandla' ekubhekaneni nalendzaba.
'Ngitiva nginemandla lamakhulu, nyalo - ngitsini-ke ngekona kwetfu kulendzaba yebulili besilisa?' kwasho yena.
'Yini lesiyifundzisa emadvodza njengobe akhula, mayelana naletinkinga lesibukene nato lamuhla?'
Kit ukholelwa kutsi iTV inendzima lenkhulu ekuvuseni kwebudvodza lobungemuhle lobuniketwa ngulabo labadvuna.
Wachubeka watsi: 'Ngukuphi lokungumuntfu lotalwa ngako nalokufundziswa ngako?
Yini lefundziswa ku-TV, nasemigwacweni, leyenta bafati bacabange kutsi kufanele babe naloluhlobo lwebantfu kute babe ngemadvodza?
Ngitsi mbamba-mbamba umbuto lomcoka kakhulu lesibukene nawo esikhatsini setfu ngukutsi - singayishintja njani?
Kungobe kuliciniso kutsi kunetintfo letingahambi kahle ngalabasha.'
Kulenkhulumo waphindze wavuma kutsi angeke adlale ku Game of Thrones nobe kulenye incenye yalenkhulumo ngesikhatsi le-serial iphela kulehlobo lelilandzelako, watsi 'sewucedzile ngetimphi nemahhashi.'
Kusukela ngaNovember Kit utawube acishe abe yinhloko ku-Sam Shepard's True West, indzaba yemkhiciti welitfole kanye nemnakabo, lobekasiphatsimandla.
Lomlingisi usandza kuveta kutsi kuhlangana nemkakhe Rose bekungulesinye setizatfu letilungile tekuphuma kuGame of Thrones.
'Ngahlangana nemkami kulomdlalo, ngabanjelwa likusasa lemndeni wami, futsi ngacala kuphila kwami' kwasho yena.
Rose udlala Ygritte, imbali yelutsandvo yelitfunti laKit, Jon Snow, kuloluhlelo lwe-Emmy-winning fantasy.
Labashadako bashada ngenyanga yeNyoni ngemnyaka wa-2018 endzaweni yasekhaya kaLeslie eScotland.
iHIV/AIDS: I-China ibika kwandza lokungu-14% kwetigameko letisha
I-China imemetele kwenyuka ngemaphesenti lalishumi nakune elinanini lebantfu labaphila ne-HIV ne-AIDS.
Bantfu labangu-820 000 bacolelwe ngulesifo kulelive, kusho tikhulu tetemphilo.
Cishe ema-40 000 emacala lamasha labikiwe ngekota yesibili ya 2018.
Linyenti laletinkinga letisandza kuvela litfolakala ngekwelicansi, lokuluphawu lwekushintja lokukhulu.
Ngekwesintfu, i-HIV isakateka ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite e-China ngenca yekumpontshelwa ingati lesele.
Kodvwa-ke, linani lebantfu labangenwa yi-HIV ngalendlela lehle lacishe laba ngu-zero, kusho tiphatsimandla tetemphilo tase-China enhlanganweni lebeyibanjelwe esifundzeni saseYunnan.
Kodvwa-ke, ngemnyaka munye linani lebantfu labaphila ne-HIV ne-AIDS e-China bese lingetulu kwa-100 000.
Kungenwa yi HIV ngekuya ecasini kuyinkinga lenkhulu esiveni sema China lesika-LGBT.
Kutsiwa kusemtsetfweni kutsi umuntfu abe ngumuntfu webulili lobufanako e-China, kwentiwa nga-1997, kepha kucalwa kwebantfu labamnyama, labadvuna nalabasikati, labamnyama nalabafana, kucalwa kwebantfu labamnyama, labamnyama nalabafana.
Ngenca yemasiko alelive leligcina lisiko, tifundvo tikhomba kutsi emadvodza langemaphesenti la-70 kuya ku-90 alala nalamadvodza agcina ngekushada nalabasikati.
Kwetfulwa lokunyenti kwaletifo kubangelwa kungativikeli ngalokwanele ekuhlanganyeleni ngekwelicansi.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende wase-China wente sivumelwano sekutsi bonkhe bantfu labanaleligciwane le HIV kufanele batfole lokwelashwa.
Maxine Waters waphika ngekutsi basebenti be GOP bacoce ngemininingwane yebasati, basakata 'emanga lamasha' kanye 'netimfundziso temikhuba'
Lisekela laMaxine Waters kuMgcibelo liphike kutsi linye lemalunga akhe lasetjentiswa etintfweni takhe letitsite letitfunyelwa ngemaphoyisa latfumela imininingwane yebantfu labatsatfu labamnyama labamnyama kumakhomishini e-Wikipedia.
I-Los Angeles Democrat Party itsi lesimemetelo besikhutsatwa ngulabo labati kakhulu kanye nema-website "alapha ngasekudla".
"Emaciniso, emanga, kanye nemanga lamabi kakhulu", Waters washo njalo kuTwitter.
Kubikwa kutsi lemininingwane leyehlukene leyehlukene ifaka ekhatsi likheli lasekhaya netinombolo telucingo te-United States Senators Lindsey Graham wase South Carolina, Mike Lee kanye na-Orrin Hatch, bonkhe basuka e-Utah.
Lolwati luvele ku-internet ngeLesine, lutfunyelwe ngumuntfu longatiwa eKapitoli Hill ngesikhatsi semhlangano welipaneli leSenate lelimelene netinsolo tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi kwelikhansela leNkantolo lePhakeme, Brett Kavanaugh.
Lokucoshwa kwavela ngemuva nje kwekutsi bomengameli labatsatfu bacele Kavanaugh.
Tikhungo letinemibono lefana ne Gateway Pundit ne RedState, tibiketele kutsi le-IP lekhomba lomtfombo walemilayeto ihlangene nelihhovisi la-Waters futsi yembule umniningwane walesisebenti sa-Waters, kusho Hill.
Watsi: "Loku lokushiwo ngulesihlubuki akusiyo intfo lokufanele siyikhumbule.
"Tisebenti tami - lobungubo bato, imininingwane yabo kanye nekuphepha kwabo kusengotini ngekusolwa ngemanga - atizange tibe nesandla ekuvulekeni kwalolwati.
Lamacala langakabekwa lawagcinwe etinhlitiyweni atinsolo letingemanga".
Lesitatimende sa-Waters sabese sibanga kuphikiswa ku-inthanethi, kufaka ekhatsi lobekangumabhalane we-White House Press Secretary Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer wabhala watsi: "Kuphikisa kusho kutfukutsela".
"Loku kusho kutsi akafaneleki kuba lilunga leKhongolose.
Nangabe umuntfu asolwa ngentfo langakayenti, akukafaneli atfukutsele.
Akukafaneli kutsi tibe nesiphetfo lesinjalo.
Akukafaneli batibute kutsi umuntfu lowenta lomsebenti wentani.
Kufanele kube nekuthula lokukhulu".
Fleischer uvele watfula imphendvulo yakhe ku Waters mayelana nekugceka kwelicembu le Democrat mayelana na Kavanaugh, lavele atfukutsele kakhulu ngesikhatsi sekuseshwa kwelicala laKuvusi.
Omar Navarro, longulomunye walabamele i-Republican Party lobekafuna kulahla Waters elukhetfweni lwema-parliamentary, naye waveta umbono wakhe ku-Twitter.
"Kuhle kakhulu nangabe kuliciniso", waveta kanjalo ku-Twitter.
Esitatimendeni sakhe, Waters watsi lihhovisi lakhe "selicaphele tiphatsimandla kanye netinhlangano letibukene nekusebenta kwemtsetfo mayelana nalokucuketfwe lokungemanga.
"Sitawucinisekisa kutsi labakwentile bayaboshwa", wachubeka, "kute batfole kutsi babhekene nelicala lelimayelana netento tabo letiyingoti naletimbi, letentiwa ngulabanye basebentisi bami".
"Johnny English Strikes Again" - incwadzi lechaza i-spy Rowan Atkinson
Kulesikhatsi lesi, kufuna kubaluleka kwe Brexit kuyinye ye-movie lensha ngekubuka lokwehlukile kwe-British sekuyintfo yesintfu futsi loko kubonakala kuyintfo lefanako ekubuyeni kwe-franchise yekuhlekisa nge-comedy yaJohnny English - lecalwa nga-2003 naJohnny English yaphindze yavuselelwa nga-2011 naJohnny English Reborn.
Kutawubese kuba yintfo lehlabako yini kutsi sitfole ematfuba lamasha ekungenisa eveni?
Noma kunjalo, Johnny English lonemehlo lagcwele inkhungu, lobuso lobugugeletako, longakhoni nekusebenta, ubuye wavusetela ilayisensi yakhe yekususa konkhe lokuhle kwesibili - ligama lakhe lisho lokunyenti kunaloko lokunyenti kutsi ungumcambi lomcoka wemafilimu lakhelwe etindzaweni letingakhulumi siNgisi.
Uyakwati kutsi uyintfo leyingoti, futsi, nangetulu kwekucindzeteleka kwakhe lokumangalisako, unemlingisi lonjengekutsi nguClouseau, umlingisi lonjengekutsi nguMnumzane Bean kanye nemlingisi lonjengekutsi nguVeliko lowaba neligalelo lelihle kakhulu emculweni we-Chariots of Fire emcimbini wekuvula i-London Olympic emcimbini wanga-2012.
Empeleni, wacala ngekuba ngumhambi futsi indvodza leyatiwa kakhulu emhlabeni wonkhe, Atkinson, bekayidlala kumakhangisi weTV we-Barclaycard, nyalo sewuyashiywa nje, ushiye ngemuva kwakhe lokudidekile.
Kunetikhatsi letimnandzi lapha JE.
Ngitsandza kubona Johnny English asondzela kulesikebhe agcoke timphahla tangesikhatsi lesidze, nemabhola esayidi ahlangana nesigcoko sakhe.
Kantsi nelikhono la-Atkinson lekuhlekisa ngemtimba liyakhonjiswa, kepha umcondvo wakhe wekuhlekisa awuniki emandla futsi unekuhlanya, ikakhulu uma emafilimu "lashubile" lafana na-007 kanye ne-Mission Impossible sekatetsemba kutsi atawufaka emagama ekuhlekisa.
Emahlaya akhe abonakala etfulelwa bantfwana kunebantfu labadzala, futsi kimi bekubonakala shengatsi Johnny English bekangatiphatsi kahle futsi bekangaboni kahle kutsi Atkinson bekangumuntfu lonjani.
Lesisekelo lesasicedza iminyaka leminyenti kutsi iNgilandi isebuhlungwini lobukhulu.
Umhlaseli we-cyber ungene ku-website lengumfihlo yemaNgisi, aveta bonk' bonkhana bemaphoyisa ase-UK, kwentela kushiya ema-agent lasemsebentini - lokubuhlungu kutsi kunendzima lencane kuKevin Eldon.
