Umeluleki wakhe lomuhle wamtjela kutsi njengobe onkhe emabutfo akhe lasebentako akhubatekile, kufanele atsatse lomunye.
Loku kusho kutsi Johnny English, lobekangasahambi kahle, nyalo sewuhleti etikwelihhovisi lelikhulu lelisetulu, kodvwa ufundzisa bantfu imfihlo yekusebenta ngephandle kwemabhizinisi: kunemahlaya lamahle lapha, lapho khona English ufundzisa khona etikolweni tekusesha, njengeSikole se-Rock.
