Bo-English na-Bough bacala kwenta tintfo tabo letingacondzakali: ngekutifihla njengetisebenti tasendlini, bashisa indzawo yekudlela yemaFrench; benta umonakalo ngekungenela umkhumbi wa-Volta; futsi bacala kungevani ngesikhatsi etama kusebentisa i-Virtual Reality headset kute atihlanganise nendzawo yaseVolta.
Tonkhe letitfombe betibutselwe kuloluhlelo lwekugcina, kepha ngekuhlanganisa lokunje, kunetindlela letimbalwa te-TV tebantfwana letiniketa konkhe.
