Yini i-Global Citizen Festival futsi ngabe loku kwente lokutsite yini ekulweni nebuphuya?
Le New York City itawube ichuba umkhosi we Global Citizen Festival, umcimbi wemnyaka ngemnyaka wetingoma letitodvwa letitodvwa letinemsebenti lomuhle, futsi letinemsebenti lojabulisako wekucedza buphuya emhlabeni.
Lomnyaka wesibili we-Global Citizen Festival utawubukela umnyakato wetinkhulungwane tebantfu letita e-Great Lawn e-Central Park hhayi nje kuphela kutojabulela umbukiso wa-Janet Jackson, Cardi B, na-Shawn Mendes, kodvwa kuphindze kwente bantfu bati ngalemigubhu lecondzile yekucedza buphuya nga-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival, lecalwa nga-2012, yintfo lelandzelako ye-Global Poverty Project, licembu le-advocacy lamazwe onkhe leletsemba kucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa linani lebantfu labalwela kulwa nebuphuya.
Kute utfole emathikithi amahhala kulomcimbi (ngaphandle nangabe ufuna kukhokhela emathikithi e-VIP), laba labakhona kulomcimbi kumele bacedze luhlu lwemisebenti nobe inyatselo letifana nekuvolontiya, kutfumela ema-imeyili kubaholi bemave, kubashayela lucingo, nobe letinye tindlela letibonakalako tekusita ekwandziseni lwati ngemgomo wabo wekucedza buphuya.
Kodvwa eminyakeni lengu-12 leyendlulile, i-Global Citizen ibe yimphumelelo lenjani ekufinyeleleni imigomo yayo?
Ngabe kucabanga ngekunikela ngemakhonsathi amahhala kuyindlela lekahle yini yekukhutsata kutibandzakanya, noma kungulenye indlela lebitwa ngekutsi ?ngumkhuba wekutsi bantfu bacabange ngekwenta umehluko ngekusayina i-petition ku-internet nobe ngekutfumela umlayeto ku-Twitter?
Kusukela nga-2011, i-Global Citizen itsi seyibhale ngetulu kwetigidzi letingu-19 "tetento" tebasekeli bayo, letigcugcutela kutsi tibekelwe letinye tinhloso.
Kutsiwa lesento sisite kucinisa baholi bemhlaba kutsi bamemetele kutibophetela netinchubomgomo letilinganiselwa ku-$37 billion letitawufaka sandla kubantfu labangetulu kwa-2.25 wetigidzigidzi ngemnyaka wa-2030.
Ekucaleni kwemnyaka wa 2018, lelicembu selihlanganise kutibophelela lokungu 390 kanye netimemetelo letiphuma emisebentini yalo, lokungaba ngemali lecishe ibe tigidzi temarandi letingu-10 leyakhiwe nobe leyakhiwe.
Lelicembu lilinganisa kutsi imali lephephile yente umtselela locondzile kubantfu labalinganiselwa kutigidzi letingu-649 mhlabawonkhe.
Tintfo letinkhulu letentiwako tifaka ekhatsi i-The Power of Nutrition, inhlangano yaseNgilandi leyakhiwe ngulabo labatsengisa ngetimali kanye netisebenti letibophelele "ekusiteni bantfwana kutsi bakhule baphumelele", leyetsenisa iRwanda imali letigidzi letingu-R35 tekusita kucedza kungadli kahle kulelive ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweets langetulu kwa-4 700 lavela ku-Global Citizen.
"Ngekusekelwa nguhulumende waseNgilandi, banikeli, bohulumende basemaveni kanye netakhamuti temhlaba wonkhe njengani, singenta kutsi kungabi khona kwebulungiswa kutekudla kube yintfo lemcoka emlandvweni", kusho Tracey Ullman, ummeli weThe Power of Nutrition, etincumeni letatihlangene emkhosini lophilako waseLondon nga-April 2018.
Lelicembu liphindze latsi ngemuva kwemikhankaso lengetulu kwa-5000 yekukhulisa kudla kwebantfu labasikati nebantfwana eNgilandi, hulumende umemetele kutsi utawucala umklamo, i-Power of Nutrition, lotawutfola tigidzi letisihlanu tebantfu labasikati nebantfwana ngekudla kwebantfwana.
Batsi nabaphendvula umbuto lophefumulelwe ku-Public Response on their website lotsi "Yini lekwenta ucabange kutsi singakhona kucedza buphuya lobegcwele emhlabeni?"
Global citizen uyaphendvula: "Loku kutawuba yindlela lendze naledzinga kuhanjwa - ngalesinye sikhatsi sitawukhuphuka futsi sehluleke.
Kodvwa, njengetintfo letimbili letinkhulu temalungelo ebantfu kanye netinhlangano letimelene nelubandlululo lebetikhona ngaphambi kwetfu, sitawuphumelela, ngobe nasicinile, sitawuphindze sibe nemandla.
