U-Ambassador waseMelika usola iChina ngekutsi 'iyakutfukutselisa' ngekukhangisa 'kwebuphrofayli'
Ngemuva kweliviki likhasi leliphephandzaba laseShayina lifake sikhangiso semakhasi lamane ku-Daily Express lesikhombisa kutsi kuhwebelana emkhatsini wase-US ne-China kuyintfo lezuzisako, lomphatsi lomkhulu wase-US e-China usola i-Beijing ngekutsi isebentisa i-American press kute isakatse inkhulumo lengemanga.
Mengameli Donald Trump waveta ngeLwesitsatfu kutsi iChina Daily yenta imali ngekubhala kuDes Moines Register - lokuliphephandaba lelikhulu lelibhicilelako e-Iowa - ngemuva kwekusola i-China ngekutsi yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwe-US Congress lwangaNovember 6, intfo lephikiswa yi-China.
Tinsolo taTrump tekutsi iBeijing yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwaseMelika, lokuyintfo leshiwo tikhulu taseMelika kuReuters, tigaba letinsha tekwenyuka kwemkhankhaso waseMelika wekucindzetela iChina.
Nanobe kuvamile kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle bakhangise kute bakhutsate kutsengiselana, iBeijing neWashington nyalo sebatimphikiswano tekutsengiselana, lokwenta kutsi bachubeke nekukhuphula intsela kulomunye nalomunye.
Kucala kwemphi yekutsengiselana, emaShayina abeka imitselo kute asuse ema-exporters emaveni lafana ne-Iowa, lesebambelele ku-Trump, kusho tati tase-China kanye netaseMelika.
Terry Branstad, lobekayincusa yaseMelika eChina kanye nalobekanguMengameli wase-Iowa, lokunguwona aphatsa kakhulu tekulima eChina, utsi iBeijing yente lokubi kubasebenti baseMelika, kubalimi, kanye nakubosomabhizinisi.
I-China, Branstad wabhala ngayo ku-Des Moines Register ngeLisontfo, " nyalo seyiphindzaphindza lokwesabisa ngekusebentisa i-propaganda emshinini wetfu lokhululekile".
Branstad wabhala watsi: "Kuchubekisa lenchubo yawo, hulumende waseChina usebentisa lisiko lekukhuluma lelikhululekile kanye nebetindzaba lelitibaluleke kakhulu eMelika ngekutsi afake tikhangisi letifanele kule-Des Moines Register".
"Ngalokwehlukile, etitolo tekutsengisa emaphephandzaba lapha eBeijing, utotfola kutsi kunemsindvo lomncane futsi awuboni kubonisana kweliciniso kwemibono leyehlukene bantfu baseChina labangaba nayo mayelana netinkinga temnotfo waseChina, njengobe emaphephandzaba alawulwa yiCPC", wabhala.
Wengeta ngekutsi "lelinye lamazwe lanemaphephandzaba lahloniphekile eChina lalahla sicelo sekushicilela" sihloko sakhe, nanobe angacondzisanga kutsi ngumuphi emaphephandzaba.
Bahloli bacala ngekucwayisa, iRepublican Party isusa embili emagama ebantfu labasikati ngembi kwekuba nesibhicongo seMtsetfo weKuvuna
Njengobe bantfu labamcoka kuRiphabhlikhi basembili futsi basekela umengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh ngekubhekana netinsolo tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi, bahloli bayecwayisa ngekutsi batawubona kuphendvuka, ikakhulukati kwebesifazane, elukhetfweni lwekucala lolutako.
Inshisekelo yekusebenta kwalesihloko seyiphakeme kakhulu, futsi liningi lemaRephabliki labhaliwe lakhombisa kutsi afuna kuvota.
Loku angeke kuvinjelwe", Grant Reeher, longuphrofesa wesayensi yetembusave ku Maxwell School, Syracuse University, watjela The Hill ngendzaba leyayikhulunywe ngaMgcibelo.
Reeher utsi uyatibuta kutsi ngabe lokwentiwa ngu (R-Arizona) Senator Jeff Flake ngesikhatsi sekuphelelwa sikhatsi kutsi i-FBI iphenye yena kutokwanela yini kutsi kwehlise lulaka lwebavoti.
"Bafati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwenteka itolo - angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa, futsi ngeke bakukhohlwe loko lokwenteka ngeLweti", kusho Karine Jean-Pierre, longumeluleki lomdzala kanye nemkhulumeli wavelonkhe welicembu lelibukeka ngendlela lephambene newetemtsetfo i-MoveOn, ngeLesihlanu, njengobe kushiwo liphephandzaba lase-Washington, D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, lababhikishi bamemeta "Kusedvute iNovember!" ngesikhatsi babhikisha egumeni leSenate ngesikhatsi emaRephabliki acosha Likomidi Lelitiko Letemtsetfo kute lihambe phambili ngekukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh nangetulu kwekufakaza kwaDkt. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ubika.
"Ligugu kanye netinhloso te demokrasi kutawucedvwa", Stu Rothenberg, longumbhali wetembusave longasekeli lutfo, watjela iNewsweek.
"Bantfu batsi seyiphakeme kakhulu; futsi iliciniso.
Kodvwa kungaphindze kube ngetulu kwaloko, ikakhulukati kulabesifazane labasemaphandleni kanye nakulabancane, labaneminyaka lengu-18 kuya ku-29 budzala, labangamtsandzi umengameli, bavame kungamvumeli kutsi aye eluhlwini lwemavoti".
Ngisho nangembikwekutsi Ford avume kuchaza ngalokusobala ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi lokwentiwa nguye ngulelicala lelikhulu, bacwaningi bayeluleka ngekutsi kutawuba nekucindzetelwa lokulandzelako uma ngabe i-Republican Party imcindzetela kutsi avume.
"Loku sekwuphelile nge GOP", Michael Steele, lobekahlele sikhulu selikomidi le Republican National Committee, watjela i-NBC News ekucaleni kweliviki.
"Loku akusiko nje kuphela mayelana nekukhetfwa kwemakomiti nobe livoti lekugcina nobe ngabe Kavanaugh utawufakwa ebhentshini, kepha mayelana nendlela emaRepublican latawubukana ngayo naloku nekutsi batawuchubeka njani", kusho Guy Cecil, umcondzisi we-Priorities USA, licembu lelisita kukhetfwa kwelicembu le-Democrats, likhomba ku-News Channel.
Kodvwa-ke, bantfu baseMelika babonakala bahlukene ekhatsi ngekutsi ngubani lokufanele bametsembe ngemuva kwaletinkhulumo taFord naKavanaugh, kantsi bakhetsa kutsi ngubani lokufanele bametsembe.
Luhlolo lolusha lolwentiwe yi-YouGov lukhombisa kutsi 41% walabo labaphendvulako bakholelwa ngalokuphelele nobe mhlawumbe bakholwe kulobufakazi ba-Ford, babe 35% batsi bayakholelwa nobe bayakholwa ku-Kavanaugh.
Kwengeta lapho, emaphesenti langu-38 atsi bacabanga kutsi Kavanaugh angacala nobe angacala emanga ngesikhatsi afakaza, kantsi emaphesenti langu-30 kuphela atsi lokufanako kuFord.
Ngemuva kwekukhutsatwa nguFlake, iFBI nyalo iphenya ngetinsolo letentiwa nguFord kanye nalomunye umbekwacala, Deborah Ramirez, kusho iThe Guardian.
Ford wafakaza ngaphansi kwesifungo phambi kwelikomidi leSenate Judiciary kutsi Kavanaugh lobekanekungcola lokumatima wamhlasela ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lelishumi nesikhombisa.
Ramirez utsi lomuntfu lotawugweba eNkantolo lephakeme waveta emagcubu akhe kuye ngesikhatsi bahambela liphathi ngesikhatsi bafundza e-Yale ngabo-1980.
Basunguli be World Wide Web bahlela kuvula i-Internet lensha kute balwisane ne-Google ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, longumsunguli we World Wide Web, ucala inkapani lefuna kumelana ne Facebook, Amazon kanye ne Google.
Umklamo wakhe lomusha, Inrupt, yinkampani leyakhiwe ngemithombo levulekile yaBerners-Lee, iSolid.
Solid uvumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi ngutiphi tintfo labatatifuna kanye nekutsi ngubani lotawutfola letintfo.
Kulencwadzi letsi "Fast Company" Berners-Lee utsi inhloso ya Inrupt "kubusa umhlaba".
"Kufanele sicale nyalo", kwasho lomsunguli.
"Lesi sikhatsi lesibalulekile".
Loluhlelo lusebentisa i-Solid technology levumela bantfu kutsi bakhe "luphiko lwabo lwe-online lwekugcina lwemininingwane" noma i-POD.
Loku lokutfutsele kungafaka ekhatsi luhla lwebantfu labatsintsekako, luhla lwetintfo lokufanele tentiwe, emakhalenda, umtapo wetincwadzi temculo kanye naleminye imiculu yemuntfu neyesisebenti.
Njengekutsi iGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, Slack, neSpotify konkhe kuyatfolakala kusiphequluli sinye ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwenta loluhla lwemniningwane lobanjiwe lube ngulona lungele kutsi umsebentisi abe nelilungelo lekufinyelela kulo.
Kulemikhakha, kwatiwa ngekutsi "kuniketwa kwemandla ngekusebentisa idatha".
Lendzaba yekusungula i-Inrupt, ngekusho kwa John Bruce, umengameli lomkhulu wale-inthanethi, bekukutsi le-inthanethi inikete ngetintfo, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele ekusiteni i-Solid kutsi itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo lelicembu lakhiwa nguBerners-Lee, Bruce, i-IBM, licembu lebasunguli labasebenta ngekucasha, kanye nelicembu letisebenti tekutitsandzela letenta luhlelo.
Kucala kuleliviki, bahleli betintfo letisetjentiswako mhlabawonkhe batawukwati kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa tintfo letisetjentiswa ngulabanye basebentisa emathuluzi latfolakala kuwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
Berners-Lee utsi yena nelicembu lakhe abazange bakhulume ne "Facebook kanye ne-Google mayelana nekutsi ngabe batawucala yini kugucula ngalokuphelele lapho khona tonkhe tinhlobo temabhizinisi abo titawujikiswa ngalokuphelele ngelilanga.
"Asizange sibacele imvume".
Kuloko lakushoko ku Medium, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi "umgomo we-Inrupt kutsi ube ngumtfombo wemandla kanye netintfo letitsengisako tekusebenta kwentela kusita ekuvikeleni bucotfo kanye nelizinga lale-web lensha leyakhiwe nge-Solid".
Nga-1994, Berners-Lee wayigucula i-Internet ngesikhatsi asungula i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kuletinyanga letimbalwa letengcile, Berners-Lee ube livi lelikhulu enkhulumeni yekungabi nekuhlanganisa.
Ngisho nangesikhatsi sekwetfulwa kwe-Inrupt, Berners-Lee bekatawuchubeka abe nguMsunguli kanye neMcondzisi we-World Wide Web Consortium, i-Web Foundation kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelihle kakhulu nge web-era lelandzelako", Berners-Lee wengeta.
Bernard Vann: Sikhumbuzo seMphini yeMhlaba Yekucala Victoria Cross
Nguye kuphela umfundisi welibandla le-Anglican lowawina i-Victoria Cross ngesikhatsi semphi yelive yekucala, njengemuntfu lobekaliwa emphini, ukhunjulwa endzaweni yakhe yekutalwa ngemuva kweminyaka lelikhulu.
Lithelamkhulamtsetfo Lemphatsi Lendvuna, Bernard Vann wawina umklomelo wakhe ngamhlaka 29 Inyoni 1918 ngekuhlaselwa eBellenglise naseLehaucourt.
Kwatsi nje ngemuva kwemalanga lamane wabulawa sisebenti lesidvuna, wangete wati kutsi bese atfole umklomelo lomkhulu waseBrithani.
Litje lesikhumbuto lelisembili lamiswa batukulu bakhe lababili emcimbini eRushden, eNorthamptonshire, ngeMgcibelo.
Lomunye wetindvodzana takhe, Michael Vann, watsi lelitje "lifanekisela buhlakani" lobutawuveta umnyaka wa-100 wekuphumelela kwekukhipha umklomelo wakhabo gogo wakhe.
Ngekusho kwe London Gazette, ngaSeptember 29, 1918, Lt Col Vann wahola libutfo lakhe ecanal de Saint-Quentin "ngekungena emnyameni lowesabekako ngaphansi kwekudubula lokukhulu kwetibhamu letisemgwacweni kanye nemishini".
Wagijima waya emgceni wekucala, "ngebungcweti bakhe" wahola lababili labadvuna, wase uvula sibhamu sakhe lesasisebentiswa nguye yedvwa, wabulala emabutfo lamatsatfu.
Lemphi yaphela ngesikhatsi Lithishanhloko Vann libulawa ngemaJalimane nga-October 4, 1918 - lokwakuyinyanga nje kuphela ngaphambi kwekutsi imphi iphele.
Michael Vann, loneminyaka lengu-72, utsi loko lokwentiwa ngulomkhulu wakhe "yintfo lengati kahle kutsi ngeke ngikhone kuyikhona kodvwa yintfo lebonakala itfobekile".
Yena kanye nemnakabo Dokotela James Vann nabo bafaka timbali ngemuva kwemcimbi, lowaholwa yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
Michael Vann utsi "kulilungelo lelikhulu kuba yincenye yalomkhankhaso" futsi uchubeka atsi "sibindzi sebuchawe mbamba siyakhonjiswa ngekusekelwa bantfu labanyenti".
Bantfu be-MMA bavuka ebusuku babuka i-Bellator 206 kodvwa babese batfola i-Peppa Pig
Asewucabange nje, uke wahlala busuku bonkhe kute ubukele i-Bellator 206 lebeyigcwele bantfu, kodvwa waphindze walahlwa kutsi ungabukeli lomdlalo.
I-San Jose's Billings icuketse timphi letingu-13, kufaka ekhatsi letisitfupha ekhadini leliphakeme futsi isakatwa-ngco ebusuku e-UK ku Channel 5.
Kwatsi ngensimbi yesitfupha ekuseni, ngesikhatsi Gegard Mousasi naRory MacDonald batilungiselela kubambana, babukeli baseNgilandi bamangala ngesikhatsi lomdlali agucuka aba nguPeppa Pig.
Labanye bantfu beva shengatsi bangakahlonishwa ngekulala sikhatsi lesidze ngelilanga lemphi.
Lomunye umlandeli kuTwitter uchaza kungena kwebantfwana kumabonakudze ngekutsi "kuhlekisa lokucansulako".
"Kungumtsetfo wahulumende kutsi, ngetikhatsi tasekuseni te-6:00, lokucuketfwe akukalungeli kutsi kungasetjentiswa, ngako-ke kucitfwa kwaletintfo letisetjentiswa kubantfwana", kusho Dave Schwartz, umengameli lomdzala we-Belllator wekumaketha nekutsintsana, nakabutwa ngalomlayeto.
"Peppa the Pig", yebo.
Umengameli we Bellator Scott Coker utsi batawukulungisa kuhlela kwabo ngekutsi bacabange ngebabukeli baseNgilandi esikhatsini lesitako.
"Ngicabanga kutsi nangabe singacabanga ngekudlala kabusha, ngicabanga kutsi singakhona kukwenta loku", kwasho Coker.
"Kodvwa nyalo kusesekuseni kakhulu, li-awa lesitfupha ngeLisontfo futsi angeke sikhone kulungisela sikhatsi setfu lesisontfo, lesikhatsi sabo lesingoMvulo.
Kodvwa tsine sisasebenta kuko.
Ngetsembeni, ngesikhatsi sekuntjintisana, kunetincwadzi letinyenti letibuya nabuya futsi letingafundzisi lutfo.
Kukhona lokungakalungi lokutawentiwa.
Cha, yintfo hulumende layicabangako.
Ngicela ungetsembe, esikhatsini lesitako angeke kwenteke.
Sitawukunciphisa lokulwa kube sihlanu kulokusitfupha - njengobe besivame kwenta - futsi sitawugwema kubukisa kakhulu kubantfu, futsi siphumelele.
Loku akusiyo nje intfo lenhle".
Tom Daley utibona 'angakabaluleki' uma kucondziswe ekuhlanganyeleni ngekwelicansi
Umgwedli we-Olympic Tom Daley utsi wakhula angakanakwa ngenca yetinkinga takhe tekuya ecasini - kodvwa loko kwamenta waba nesibindzi sekuphumelela.
Lomuntfu loneminyaka lelishumi nakune budzala utsi akazange akubone loko kwenteka waze waya ekolishi, watsi "Akusibo bonkhe bantfu labanjengami".
Akhuluma kwekucala nje ku Radio 4's Desert Island Discs lapho ahamba naLauren Laverne, watsi ukhuluma ngemalungelo ebantfu labashadile kutsi anike labanye "litsemba".
Waphindze watsi kuba ngumtali akubenti kutsi abe nekuciniseka ngekuncoba lemidlalo.
Umengameli walelicembu lelisolo lisebenta sikhatsi lesidze, Kirsty Young, utsatse tinyanga letimbalwa atsatse liholide ngenca yekugula.
Kulesikhatsi sekubekwa kwakhe ku-TV, Daley watsi utiva "angekho ezingeni" lebantfu labadzala labebaphila naye ngobe "akusiko lokuhle kutsi utsandze emadvodza nobe bafati".
Utsi: "Kuze kube ngulamuhla, leyo miva yekungabi nalutfo kanye nekwehlukahlukana, ngiko kanye lokungicalile lokunginiketa emandla ekwenta loko".
Abefuna kukhombisa kutsi "uyintfo letsite", atsi, kute angadvumateki nakubonwa kutsi unetinkinga ngekwebulili.
Lomdlali lowatfola ema-bronze lamabili emidlalweni yema-Olympic, sewungumkhankaso lowatiwako we-LGBT, futsi usebentisa loku lokwentiwe kulomnyaka e-Australia, emidlalweni yema-Commonwealth, kute atise emave lamanyenti kutsi angahlukunyetwa.
Watsi ukhuluma ngobe utiva anenhlanhla yekuphila akhululekile ngaphandle kwekubhekana nemiphumela, futsi ufuna kuniketa labanye "litsemba".
Lomdlali welive lonemachinga lamatsatfu utsi kutsandzana nendvodza - umcambi wemafilimu waseMelika Dustin Lance Black, lahlangana naye nga-2013 - "kungimangalise kakhulu".
Daly ushade umklomelo we-Oscar, umdzala kunaye ngeminyaka lengemashumi lamabili, futsi utsi kwehlukana ngebudzala akusiyo inkinga.
"Nangabe uhlangabetana netinkinga letinyenti kangaka usemncane" - wacala kubamba umncintiswano wakhe wekucala ngineminyaka lengu-14 budzala kantsi uyise washona nge-cancer ngemuva kweminyaka lemitsatfu - utsi kulukhuni kutfola umuntfu loneminyaka lefanako nalobekahlukubete ngetinkinga letifana naleti.
Labashadikazi bebabe nebatali nga June, ngendvodzana lebitwa ngekutsi ngu Robert Ray Black-Daley, futsi Daley utsi "umbono wakhe wonkhe" sewugucukile.
"Nangabe bengibuta mine kulomnyaka lophelile, bekutawuba ngimi lotakwenta loko, 'ngidzinga kuhlula lomchako weligolide,'" washo njalo.
"Uyati, kunetintfo letinkhulu kakhulu kunekuphumelela umdvwebo wegolide kuma-Olympic.
Umklomelo wami weligolide lema-Olympic nguRobbie".
Indvodzana yakhe inegama lelifanako neyise Robert, lowashona nga 2011 aneminyaka lengu 40 ngemuva kwekutfola kutsi unekhensa yebucopho.
Daley utsi babe wakhe akakhumbuli kutsi utawufa, futsi intfo yekugcina layitsandzako bekukutsi ngabe sebamtsengisele litikiti te-Olympic yase-London ya-2012 - ngobe abefuna kuhlala emgceni wekucala.
"Angeke ngikwati kumtjela kutsi 'Awukafaneli uhlale etulu, babe,'" washo njalo.
"Ngatigcina tandla takhe ngesikhatsi ayekela kuphefumula futsi angizange ngime ngize ngife, ekugcineni ngabona kutsi bekangehluleki", kwasho yena.
Umnyaka lolandzelako wafika emidlalweni yema Olympic ya 2012 lapho khona wawina ligolide.
Watsi: "Lengikwatiko kutsi loku ngukona bengisolo ngifisa kukwenta kuphila kwami konkhe - kutsi ngibe khona embikwesive lesiningi emidlalweni yema-Olympic, kute lokuhle kwendlula loku".
Loku kwaphindze kwaletsa kutsi acale kukhetsa ingoma yakhe yekucala, Proud by Heather Small, lebeyivele icuketse indlela yakhe yekulungiselela ema-Olympics futsi lebeyisolo imenta ahloniphe.
Desert Island Discs is a BBC Radio 4 programme that airs on Sundays at 11:15 BST. Umsebenti we-BBC wesikhatsi sasemini (Lisontfo) usebenta ngeSonto kusihlwa, li-awa lelishumi nakubili (11.15 BST) kuya kusihlwa.
Mickelson uyawugucula lomsebenti wakhe nakubukwa i-Ryder Cup ngalomgcibelo
Sikhulu seligilebhu seligilebhu saseMelika Phil Mickelson bekumele abeke lirekhodi ngeLisontfo ngesikhatsi adlala emdlalweni wakhe we-47 we-Ryder Cup, kepha bekumele ashintje sikhundla sakhe kute agweme kwenta lokubi.
Mickelson, lotawudlala kulomdlalo wemnyaka wesibili kute kube sekucaleni umlandvo wesi-12, ulandzelwe ngukaputeni Jim Furyk kumdlalo webhola yetibhola letine kanye nelicembu lelingu 4 ngeMgcibelo.
Esikhundleni sekutsi abe semdvumeni, njengobe abevame kwenta nakubo bonkhe labantfu baseMelika, lomdlali lodlala indzima yekucala futsi lotawukhipha umklomelo kahlanu, ucitse sikhatsi sakhe emkhatsini wekutsi abe ngumholi wekomidi kanye nekudlala ngalendlela latayidlala, futsi loko wakwenta ngesizatfu sekutsi abefuna kulungisa tintfo letitamenta wativa aphansi.
Akakaze abe ngumshayi locondzile ngisho nangesikhatsi sekuphakama kwemsebenti wakhe, lendvodza leneminyaka lengu-48 budzala beyingakulungeli kugibela lelicembu lelicinile le-Le Golf National, lebeyivame kuniketa sijeziso lesidze futsi lesibuhlungu nakushaywa liphutsa.
Kantsi futsi nasesikhaleni sakhe, bekungasiko lokwetfusako kuMickelson, emdlalweni wakhe wesitsatfu ngeLisontfo, lapho abukane nemncobi lomkhulu we-English Open, Francesco Molinari, lobekasebentisane naTommy Fleetwood, lomusha, kute ancobe imidlalo yakhe lemine kuleliviki.
Uma lomdlali waseMelika, acala umdlalo wakhe wesibili ngemaphuzu lamane ngaphansi, acala ngemandla, umdlalo waMickelson utawuba ngulobalulekile.
Furyk abecabanga ngalendvodza, hhayi ngobe bekanelwati lolunyenti.
"Ubevele uyicondze kahle indzima yakhe ngalelo langa, wangishaya emhlane wangigona, wangitjela kutsi utawube alungele umdlalo kusasa", kusho Furyk.
"Bekangumuntfu lotigcabha kakhulu.
Uyingcenye yelikhetselo lemagama futsi wente lokunyenti kulelicembu esikhatsini lesengcile, nakuleliviki.
Mhlawumbe angikate ngimbone kutsi udlala imidlalo lemibili.
Ngicabanga kutsi labanye bangahle bakhone, kodvwa nguloko kanye lokwentiwako, futsi nguloko kanye lesikubonile kutsi kufanele sikwente.
Ufuna kujabulela lokunye lokwehlukile, lokufana nalokwentwa ngulabanye bantfu".
Mickelson utawugcwala lirekhodi laNick Faldo lekuyindzawo lenkhulu yekudlala i-Ryder Cup ngeLisontfo.
Loku kungaveta kuphela kwemsebenti wakhe we Ryder Cup longeke uphindze ufike ezingeni lelisetulu lelisetulu lemsebenti wakhe.
Mickelson uncobe ema- 18 , uncobe ema-20 , uncobe ema- 7 , kodvwa Furyk utsi kuncoba kwakhe kuletsa tintfo letitsite kuleli cembu.
"Uyahlekisa, unengcondvo lenhle, uhlekisa, utsandza kuhlabela, futsi unemusa ekamelweni lakhe", washo achaza.
"Ngicabanga kutsi labadlali labasebancane bajabulile naye, kuleli viki, lokuyintfo lejabulisako kuyibona.
Usinikete lokunyenti kwendlula nje kudlala nje".
Sikhulu saseYurophu, Thomas Bjorn, besati kutsi tintfo letinkhulu tingalahleka ngekushesha.
Thomas Bjorn, longukaputeni waseYurophu, wafundza ngekutibonela kutsi umuntfu loholako ngalokwanele emdlalweni wakhe wekugcina we-Ryder Cup, angaba nguloluhambo lolungemnandzi.
Lenkhebe yacala umdlalo wayo wekucala nga 1997 eValderrama, lapho khona indvuna yayo Seve Ballesteros beyibambe ngemaphuzu lasihlanu iMelika, kepha beyisandza kufika emgceni wekugcina ngemphumelelo yayo lemincane, incobe i-141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Uhlala utikhumbuta kutsi sinemaphuzu lamakhulu eValderrama; sinemaphuzu lamakhulu eBrookline, lapho sincobe khona, futsi sinephuzu lelikhulu eValderrama, lapho sincobe khona, kodvwa nyalo", kwasho Bjorn, atsatsa sitfombe, ngemuva kwekubuka Class of 2018, bancoba 5-3 ngaLesihlanu nangalobusuku ngekucondzisa 10-6 eLe Golf National.
Ngako umlandvo utawukhombisa kutsi mine kanye nelicembu letfu asikaze sicedze.
Kusasa kutawuba nemdlalo lomnandzi lotawuba nesitunge.
Phuma wente konkhe lokuhle.
Akupheli nawusete emaphuzu.
Sinemgomo, futsi lomgomo kutsi sincobe lomklomelo, futsi nguloko lokugcile.
Ngihlale ngitsi ngigcile kulabalishumi nakubili, kodvwa siyakwati naloko lokukhona kulabanye - labadlali labakhulu kakhulu emhlabeni".
Bjorn utsi: "Bengingeke ngikwati kugibela ngingedvwa.
Kusasa ngilo lilanga lehlukile.
