Manje, ushiye umuntfu losebenta naye futsi kufanele ahambe kute atfole lokuncono kakhulu".
Ngekungafani naBjorn, umcashi wakhe Jim Furyk bekacela badlali bakhe kutsi badlale kancono ngekwehlukana kwabo kunaloko labakwentako njengemacembu, ngaphandle kwaJordan Spieth naJustin Thomas, laba labawina lamatsatfu kulamane emaphuzu.
