"Ngikhumbula onkhe lamavi", washo aphendvula umbuto mayelana nendlela Ben Crenshaw, lobekaphetse nga-1999, lahlanganisa ngayo leticumbi takhe ngemalanga akhe ekugcina.
"Sinemidlalo lemitsatfu lebalulekile lelishumi nakubili kusasa, kodvwa ufuna kuyisheshisa njengobe ubonile eBrookline, njengobe ubonile eMedina.
Uma umfutfo uhamba ngendlela yinye, loko kungenta umfutfo lomkhulu emdlalweni.
Sesihlele nekuhlela luhlelo lwebadlali bese sifaka labantfu ngetindlela letehlukene ngendlela lesenta sitsi, niyati, setama kwenta lokumangalisako kusasa".
