Imikhumbi lemisha yemasotja aseJalimane imisiwe
Kwatsiwa lomkhumbi lomusha wase-Germany lotawungena emisebentini nga-2014 esikhundleni semikhumbi lemidzala ye-Cold War, kodvwa angeke ube khona kute kube ngunyaka lotako ngenca yetintfo letingahambi kahle kanye netindleko letisetulu, kusho imisakato yalapha.
Kusetjentiswa kwe "Rheinland-Pfalz", sikebhe lesikhulu sesikebhe lesisha se-Baden-Wuerttemberg, sekubambeliwe kuze kube yinyanga yekucala yemnyaka wa-2019, ngekusho kweliphephandzaba iDie Zeit lelicuketse sikhulumi semasotja.
Lomkhumbi bekumele ngabe ujoyine iNavy nga-2014, kepha tinkinga tekutfulwa kwato tibe tiphazamisa likusasa lalephrojekthi lebeyinelisu.
Lemikhumbi lemine yeBaden-Wuerttemberg leyacelwa ngemnyaka wa 2007 itawufika njengentfo letawubuyisela sikebhe lesidzala se Bremen.
Lelikhumbi litawube linemishini lecinile yekulwa, imishini lehlasela tibhamu letibheke etulu, kanye nemishini lehlasela imikhumbi, kanye naletinye tintfo letingabonakali, njengekucima ema-radar, ema-infrared kanye nemakhiya ekuvala.
Lokunye lokubalulekile kufaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekunakekelwa - kumele kukhone kusebentisa umkhumbi lomusha wekugadza iminyaka lemibili ungekho endzaweni lapho ukhicitelwa khona.
Kodvwa-ke, kuhamba kancane kwato bekusho kutsi lemikhumbi lemikhulu yemphi - lebeyitsi iyasita eJalimane kutsi ibonise emandla ayo kulamanye emave - beyingete yasebenta ngesikhatsi seyicala kuba khona, kusho i-Zeit.
Likhumbi lelingasiyo i-F125 lelingasiyo i-F125 laphindze lacala kukhulunywa ngalo ngemnyaka lowengcile, ngesikhatsi i-German Navy imisa ngalokusemtsetfweni kuhoxiswa kwalo lomkhumbi bese ibuyiselwa emuva e-Blohm & Voss shipyard lese Hamburg.
Bekukwekucala kutsi sikebhe semkhumbi sibuyiselwe kumakhi waso ngemuva kwekutsi sihanjiswe.
Tizatfu tekutsi kungani lelikhumbi lamasotja labuya atiwa kancane, kepha emaJalimane asho kutsi kunetinkinga letinkhulu kuletintfo letisebentako letingazange tibe lusito.
Lenkinga yekusebentisa luhlelo lwekuhlela tintfo ibalulekile ngobe le Baden-Wuerttemberg-class itawusetjentiswa ngemasotja la-120 - lokungaba nguhhafu wemisebenti yemasotja lamadzala aseBremen-class.
Kantsi futsi kufanele wati kutsi sisindvo lesisetulu salomkhumbi sesikukhulu kakhulu kutsi singasenta siphumelele futsi sivimbe kutsi sikhone kukhulisa lomkhumbi esikhatsini lesitako.
I-Rheinland-Pfalz lengemathani langu-7 000 ikholelwa kutsi inesisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesemphini yemikhumbi lefanako leyasetjentiswa ngemaJalimane eMphini yeMhlaba Yesibili.
Ngetulu kwetintfo letincane lebetingekho kahle, tindleko letinkhulu tekukhicita - lokufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti - nako bekungasilo lutfo.
Kwabe sekubikwa kutsi kukhuphuke ngemandla kwatsi kufika ku-€3.1 billion ($3.6 billion) - kusuka ekucaleni kwa-€2.2 billion.
Lenkinga yalamanti yakamuva ibaluleke kakhulu ngekunaka lesigameko lesisandza kwenteka ngekweca emandla emkhumbi wemaJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, lobekacondzisa likomidi letivikela lelisemtsetfweni laseJalimane, wavuma kutsi imikhumbi yemasotja "iphelelwe ngemikhumbi lengasebenta ngalokuphelele".
Lesikhulu satsi njengobe sikhatsi sichubeka, lenkinga beyiba yimbi kakhulu, ngobe tikebhe letindzala betingasasetjentiswa futsi bekute tikebhe letinsha letatfolwa.
Wativa buhlungu kutsi kute ngisho munye wemikhumbi lecondzene nekuphepha yeBaden-Wuerttemberg lotawungenela Lwandle.
I-National Trust yalalela imfihlo yemphilo yemabhamane ngekuthula
Lucwaningo lolusha lolwentiwe endzaweni lehlanyelwe eScotland lutawukhombisa kutsi emalulwane asebentisa indzawo lenjani nakufunwa kudla.
Kutawutsiwa loku kutokhanyisa indlela lemagciwane letiphatsa ngayo tilwane letiphilako letihamba emoyeni futsi kusite ekucondziseni imisebenti yesikhatsi lesitako.
Lolucwaningo lolwentiwe bososayensi be National Trust for Scotland, lutotsatsa indlela ye pipistrelle, soprano kanye ne Daubenton long-eared bat, e-Inverewe Gardens eWester Ross.
Emabhathini latsetfwe ngalokunjalo atawugcinwa etindzaweni letisemaphandleni.
Basebenti be-NHS kanye nemavolontiya batawenta luhlolo lweselula ngekusebentisa ema-handheld detectors.
Tati temsindvo letihlatiya onkhe lamafilimu titawucinisekisa kutsi lelibhele liyakhala kangakanani nekutsi nguyiphi inhlobo yebhejane leyenta lomsebenti.
I-HUMP ichaza kutsi kunekulingana lokukhona emkhatsini wetilwane letincane letiphilako kanye netilwane letiphilako.
Rob Dewar, longumeluleki wetekulondvolotwa kwemvelo we-NTS, unetsemba kutsi lolucwaningo lutawuveta kutsi ngutiphi tindzawo letibalulekile letigcinelwa timfene nekutsi letilwane tiwasebentisa njani.
Lolwati lutakusita kutsi ubone kutsi nguyiphi inzuzo leletfwa ngumsebenti wekunakekela indzawo lefana nekwakha indzawo lenetjani kanye nendlela lekahle yekunakekela emahlatsi alamahlatsi kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nawo.
Emabutfo ase Scotland kanye nelaseNgilandi ancipha kakhulu ngeminyaka lelikhulu leyengcile.
Leti tilwane tibekwa engotini ngekwakhiwa kwetindlu kanye nekukhula lokutsintsa tindzawo tato kanye nekulahlekelwa indzawo yato.
Tintfo letinjenge-wind turbines kanye nemibane nako kuletsa tingoti, njengekubamba emabhampa, kusebentisa emakhemikhali ekwakheni kanye nekuhlaselwa ngemakati.
Ecinisweni, emalulwane akaboni.
Kodvwa-ke, njengobe leligwaja litidla ebusuku, tindlebe talo tiligugu kunemehlo alo ekubambeni kudla.
Tisebentisa tindlela tekutfola tindzawo letinemaphimbo kute tibe kahle etintfweni letitfutfukako.
I-NTS, lenakekela takhiwo letingu-270 letinemlandvo, nemapaki langu-38 kanye nemahekitha emhlaba langu-76 000 eveni lonkhe, inendzaba kakhulu naloluhlaka lwemabhubesi.
Inetisebenti letilishumi leticeceshiwe, letichuba luhlolo lwekuhlola, luhlolo lwesikhukhukati, kanye nemisebenti yekuhlangana.
Lenhlangano iphindze yasungula lendzawo yekucala futsi leyodvwa eScotland, iThreave Plantation lese Dumfries nase Galloway, lekhaya lalabasiphohlongo kuletishumi tetinhlobo temagundvwane eScotland.
Umphatsi welikhaya lalabogwaja, David Thompson, utsi lendzawo iyindzawo lekahle yemigundatjana.
"Lapha eThreave, sinelibala lelihle lemfishi", washo njalo.
"Sinezakhiwo letinkhulu, tihlahla letindzala, kanye netindzawo letinhle.
Kodvwa kunyenti lesingakwati ngema-bat, ngako umsebenti lesiwentako lapha kanye nakuletinye tindzawo utasisita kutsi sikucondze kancono loko lokudzingwa ngulamalukatana kute akhule".
Uphindze agcizelele kutsi kumele ahlolwe emagundvwane ngaphambi kwekutsi agcinwe endzaweni letsite, ngobe uma ngabe kuvele ingwenya yinye, ingase ibulale emagundvwane lamakhulu lamane, lokungabulala bonkhe bantfu bakuleyo ndzawo.
Emagciwane elulwane avikelekile futsi kubulala, kuhlukubeta nobe kuphatamisa noma kubhubhisa tilwane tekufuywa kwawo, akukho emtsetfweni.
Elisabeth Ferrell, losisebenti seScotland seKonga i-Butterfly Trust, ukhutsata umphakatsi kutsi ufake sandla.
Utsi: "Sisenalokunyenti lokusamele sifundze ngako ngemalulwane etfu kanye nangetilwane letinyenti lesingati kutsi tiphila kuphi".
