I-Brexit: I-British itawuhlale ililela' ngekushabalala kwebakhiciti bemoto
I-British "itawutivela buhlungu" uma ilahlekelwa sikhundla sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba ngekukhicita timoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit, kusho iNdvuna yeLitiko Letemabhizinisi Greg Clark.
Wengeta watsi "kuyakhatsateka" kutsi i-Toyota, i-UK itjele i-BBC kutsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwetinjongo tekusebenta, itawuyekela umkhicito wayo eBurnaston, edvute nase Derby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwane", kwasho Mnumzane Clark.
Umcashi waseJapan utsi kubambelele emnyeleni, uma kungabikho kwekuhlanganyela, kutawufaka iBrexit engotini ngekwentsengo yemsebenti.
Sikhungo lesise Burnaston - lesakha iAuris kanye ne-Avensis, lekungimkhicito weToyota - sikhicite cishe timoto letingu-150 000 emnyakeni lophelile, letingu-90% wato letitfunyelwa e-EU.
"Ngumbono wami kutsi uma iBrithani iphuma ku EU ekupheleni kwaMashi, sitobona kuyekela kwekukhicita etitolo tetfu", kusho Marvin Cooke, longumcondzisi weToyota eBurnaston.
Labanye bakhiciti bemoto baseNgilandi bakhombisa kukhatsateka ngekutsi bangaphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sekutsi kutawuchutjwa njani, kufaka ekhatsi iHonda, iBMW kanye neJaguar Land Rover.
Sibonelo, iBMW itsi itasivala lesitolo sayo seMini e-Oxford ngemuva kwetinyanga letimbalwa i-Brexit icalile.
Inkinga lenkhulu lehlobene naloku, lekutsiwa bakhi bemoto, nguletibopho temikhicito uma ngabe kungekho kuvunyelwana nge-Brexit.
Umkhakha wetintfo te Toyota usebenta ngekuya kwemgomo wekukhicita "ngesikhatsi", netincenye letitfolwa njalo ngemizuzu lengemashumi lamatsatfu nesikhombisa kusuka kubantfu labatsengisa nge United Kingdom kanye ne European Union, kwentela lemoto leyakhiwe ngendlela yekwenta.
Uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano nga-March 29, kungahle kube nekungalingani eminyeleni, lokucatjangwa timboni kutsi kungenta kubambelele futsi kube nekweswelakala kwetinsimbi.
Kutawubese kuba lukhuni ngeToyota kutsi igcine timphahla tekusebenta telilanga linye e-Derbyshire, kusho lommeli wale nkampani, ngako-ke umkhicito utawuyekelwa.
Clark utsi luhlelo lwe-Chequers lwa Theresa May lolumayelana nebudlelwane ne-EU esikhatsini lesitako "lufanele kutsi lugcinwe lucinisekise kutsi luyakugwema kuhlolwa eminyeleni".
"Kufanele sente sivumelwano. Sifuna kwenta sivumelwano lesikahle kakhulu lesitawuvumela loko lengikushoko kutsi kungabi nje kuphela kwenjabulo yetfu yesikhatsi sanyalo, kodvwa kube setimeni tetfu tekutfola lamatfuba", kusho yena kuloluhlelo lweToday lwe BBC Radio 4.
"Loku kufakazela lokungasiko kwe Toyota kuphela kodvwa nekulabanye bakhiciti, kutsi kufanele sikhone kuchubeka naloko lokusele kungumkhicito lophelele".
I-Toyota angeke isho kutsi loku kukhicitwa kutawumiswa sikhatsi lesidze kangakanani, kodvwa kuyakhanya kutsi esikhatsini lesidze, kucwayisa kutsi imali lengetiwe itawucindzetela kubangeneli betimboni futsi ekugcineni itawuletsa kubandzeteleka kwetisebenti.
Peter Tsouvallaris, losisebente eBurnaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi losebenta njenge-unit manager kulesitolo, utsi emalunga aso abese ayakhatsateka: "Ngekubona kwami, uma lomsebenti sewuphelile, angeke uphindze ubuye.
Sikhulumi sahulumende sitsi: "Sente luhlelo loluphelele lolusebentako loluhlela budlelwano betfu ne-European Union esikhatsini lesitako".
Umhlangano wa Trump naRosenstein kungenteka kutsi uphindze ubekwe ngemuva kwesikhatsi, kusho iNdlu yeMhlophe.
Umhlangano wa Donald Trump lotawubambisana nemmeli lomkhulu Rod Rosenstein "ungahlehliselwa emuva ngeliviki" njengoba umcimbi wekukhetfwa kwa Brett Kavanaugh umengameli welicembu lelikhulu wetemtsetfo usachubeka, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein ubuke umsebenti welikhansela lelikhetsekile Robert Mueller, leliphenya ngekuhlanganyela kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini webalekeleli baTrump kanye neRussia, kanye nekuhlanganyela kwebugebengu lobentiwa ngumengameli.
Lokungabata kutsi Trump utawucosha umshushisi lomcoka, lokutawubeka inkhululeko yaMueller engotini, sekuyindzaba lephikiswako eWashington tinyanga.
Ekucaleni kwale nyanga, iNew York Times ibike kutsi Rosenstein ucoce ngekusebentisa i-telegram kucocisana naTrump kanye nekungaba khona kweliphoyisa lemengameli ngekweliphuzwana le-25 le-Amendment.
Rosenstein akakuvumi loko.
Kodvwa ngaLesibili lophelile waya eWhite House, emkhatsini wetindzaba tekutsi utawuyekela.
Ngakulolunye luhlangotsi, umhlangano naTrump, lobesekadze ukadze unendzawo ehhovisi le UN eNew York, wabekwa kutsi ube ngeLesine.
Trump watsi "angeke akhetse" kutsi Rosenstein asuswe, kepha lomhlangano wabese uyahlehliswa kuze kugwenywe kungcubutana ngekulalelwa kwekomidi yeSenate lapho khona Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye walabasikati labamsola ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, Dokotela Christine Blasey Ford, bobabili bebatawetfula bufakazi.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump ucele luhlolo lweliviki lwe-FBI ngetinsolo letimelene naKavanaugh, lokwabese kuba yintfo lehlehliswa livoti leliphelele laseSenate.
Sarah Sanders, longumabhalane we-Trump, uvela ku-Fox News Sunday.
Wambuta mayelana nekuhlangana kwakhe naRosenstein, watsi: "Lusuku lwekuhlangana alukagcwaliseki, mhlawumbe kungakapheli leliviki, kepha ngiyabona kutsi kuhle kutsi sihlehlisele emuva liviki, uma sibuka lokunye lokwenteka eNkantolo lePhakeme.
Kodvwa kutawutsiwani, futsi ngihlale ngifuna kuniketa tindzaba letisha kubemaphephandzaba".
Labanye betindzaba batawuphikisa lombono: Sanders akakasho lutfo ngetindzaba takhe eNdlini leMhlophe kusukela ngaSeptember 10.
Umengameli wetfu, Chris Wallace, ubuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders watsi lokungahlangani kahle kwebantfu bekungasiko kutsi bekangafuni kutsi babhale tindzaba kumabonakudze "lebetama kubamba umcimbi", noma kunjalo, watsi: "Angivumelani nekutsi betama kubamba umcimbi".
Wabese uphakamisa kutsi kuchumana lokucondzile emkhatsini waTrump nemaphephandzaba kufanele kuciniswe.
"Baphatsi belibandla babamba tinkhulumo letichubekako kunebantfu labake baphatsa", washo akhuluma ngaphandle kwekusho bufakazi: "Sesivele siwabonile lamagama".
Sanders utsi lomhlangano usetawuchubeka, kodvwa "uma nje emaphoyisa akhona kubuta umbiko kumengameli waseMelika, loko kuncono kakhulu kunekukhuluma nami.
Senta imetamo yekwenta loku kaningi futsi niyakubona kutsi sente kaningi kuleliviki leliphelile futsi loko kutawutsatsa sikhundla setinkhulumo tetindzaba uma nikhona kucoca nemengameli waseMelika".
Trump uvame kubuta imibuto nakaphuma e-White House nobe nakahambela tikhulu.
Tinhlangano tebabiketi letite muntfu ativami kutsi tibanjwe.
Kuleliviki leliseNew York, Mengameli utawuveta sizatfu sakhe, ngekwenta umbukiso longakavami nalongakavami ngaphambi kwekutsi kwetfulwe netintsatseli.
Bhala incwadzi leya kubasebenti base-EU ku-NHS Scotland ukhombisa kukhatsateka nge-Brexit
INdvuna yeTemphilo ibhale incwadzi leya kubasebenti base-EU labasebenta ku-NHS yaseScotland, ibonga live labo futsi ifisa kutsi basale basebenta ngemuva kwekwehlukana ne-UK.
Jeane Freeman MSP utfumela incwadzi lemincane lengaphansi kwetinyanga letisitfupha i-UK ishiye i-EU.
Hulumende waseScotland utibophelele kuhlangabetana netindleko tekufaka sicelo semvumo yekuhlala yalomphelo yebahlali base-EU labacashwa etisebentini temphakatsi labatfunyelwe ngaphandle.
Encwadzini yakhe, Nn Freeman wabhala: "Kulelihlobo, tinkhulumo emkhatsini we-UK ne-EU mayelana nekushiya tikhungo tato, betisondzele esiphetfweni lebesilindzelwe kulenyanga yeMphala.
Hulumende waseNgilandi utibambile uma kungahambi kahle kwe-NCA.
