I-Palu iyinhloko dolobha yesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, itfolakala ekugcineni kwechweba loluncane loluseceleni lentsentshonalanga yesichingi sase Sulawesi, inebantfu labacatjangelwe labangu 379,800 ngebantfu nga 2017.
Ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami, lelidolobha beligubha iminyaka lengu-40 yalo.
I-Donggala, yona, yindzawo lenkhulu leyakhiwe ngetigodzi letingaba ngemakhilomitha langetulu kwa-300 (180 mi) elwandle lolusenyakatfo-nshonalanga yesichingi sase Sulawesi.
Lesifundza, lesisetulu esifundzeni, sihlelwe kutsi sibe nebantfu labangu 299 200 ngemnyaka wa 2017.
Umnotfo losemcoka walesigodzi yiNhlonhlo yase Donggala.
Kodvwa-ke, imayini ye-nickel nayo ibalulekile kulesigodzi, nanobe incike kakhulu eMorowali, lesendzaweni lengaselwandle yase Sulawesi.
