Nati letinye tetingoti letinkhulu letibangelwe kutamatama kwemhlaba nematsunami kuleminyaka lembalwa leyendlulile:
NgaDecember 26, 2004, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu e-Indonesia lokwahlasela luhlavu lwendzawo leseningizimu ye-Aceh esifundzeni lesise-North Sumatra, lokuyintfo leyenta kutsi kube ne-tsunami leyasakateka emaveni langu-14, futsi kwabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-226,000 ngaselugwini loluselwandle i-Indian Ocean, futsi laba labangetulu kwehhafu yalabantfu labafa kwaba yi-Aceh.
Nga-2005: Ekupheleni kwa-March nasekucaleni kwa-April, kwenteka kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwahlasela luhlangotsi lwangasenshonalanga lwelwandle lwaseSumatra.
Bantfu labanyenti bafa ngesikhatsi lesihlahla siphelela esichingini saseNias, lesingasenseveni yaseSumatra.
Nga-2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla nga-6,8 kwehla eningizimu yeJava, lokuyindzawo lenkhulu kunato tonkhe tase-Indonesia, kwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami leyabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-700.
Nga-2009: Kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwaba ngu-7.6 ngasePadang, lokulidolobha lelikhulu lesifundza saseSumatra.
Bantfu lababalelwa ku-1 100 babulawa nguletifo.
Nga-2010: Kuzamazama kwemhlaba lokwaba ngu-7,5 kuhlasela sihlenge saseMentawai, lesiseSumatra, kwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami leyayingemamitha lalishumi, leyasusa emadolobhana lamanyenti futsi yabulala bantfu labangu-300.
2016: Regency Pidie Jaya, Aceh, nayo yahlushwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabeka umonakalo lomkhulu, kanye nekwesaba lokukhulu kwebantfu lokwabangelwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabulala bantfu labanyenti kanye ne-tsunami nga-2004.
Nanobe bekungekho tsunami, bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 babulawa ngulesiphepho.
Nga-2018: Lombok, lelitiwa ngekutsi yi-tourist island, yahlushwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, labanyenti babo lebebasenyakatfo yalesichingi.
Lokutamatama kwemhlaba kwabhidlita tinkhulungwane tetakhiwo futsi kwafaka tinkhulungwane tetivakashi.
