Palin ubhekene nemiphumela lemitsatfu yekwephulwa kwemtsetfo welicembu A, lokungamenta kutsi aphelele umnyaka munye ejele kanye nemali lengu-R250,000.
Kantsi, uphindze wabekwa licala lelibovu le-Class B, lekujeziswa lilanga linye ejele kanye nenhlawulo lengu-R2 000.
Akusiko kwekugcina kutsi Palin abekwe licala.
Ngenyanga yeNgongoni emnyakeni wa 2017, wabekwa licala ngekuhlukunyetwa kwababe wakhe, Todd Palin.
Bekunguye lowatjela emaphoyisa ngalesifo.
Umtsetfo we-Alaska Veterans Court nyalo sewusemtsetfweni.
Ngenyanga yaNgci nga 2016, wabekwa licala lekudlwengula emakhaya, kuvimbela kubikwa kwelicala lekudlwengula emakhaya, kanye nekutsatseka kwetibhamu, lokuyintfo lehlobene naloku.
Umngani wakhe utsi umshayile.
Ngemnyaka wa 2016, Sarah Palin wabekwa licala ngema vetsetsets ngoba bekachaza kutsi indvodzana yakhe inesifo se-PTSD lesasenta sesimkhatsata kakhulu umsebenti wayo e-Iraq.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka e-Indonesia: kwabulala bantfu labanyenti
