Emandla agesi kanye netekuchumana kuvele kwaphela, kantsi linani lebantfu labashonile litawukhula kulamalanga letako.
Lesihlabatsi lesingaka sagadla eSulawesi leseNshonalanga neJakarta, lokulidolobha lelikhulu laseIndonesia.
Ema-video lamanyenti lachaza indlela lesiholelo lesaba sibi ngayo, asakateka etindzaweni letinyenti tekuchumana.
Emakhulu ebantfu bekahlangene emkhosini waselwandle edolobheni lasePalu ngalesikhatsi kuvela tsunami.
Umshushisi wahulumende welwela kutfola sigwebo lesibekiwe lesingakavami sekuhlaselwa kwebantfu baseNew York.
Tishushisi te-Federal di New York tifuna kubulala Sayfullo Saipov, lobekahlelwe ngekuhlaselwa kwe-terror di New York City, lapho kwafa bantfu labasiphohlongo - lokuyintfo lengakavami futsi lengakaze yenteke ku-federal di kusukela nga-1953.
Saipov, loneminyaka lengu-30 budzala, usolwa ngekucala inhlekelele yekushayisa iloli yakhe layikhetsile leyayisuka e-Home Depot, yabhidlita bantfu labahamba ngetinyawo nebagibeli bemabhayisikili emgwacweni lowendlula ngase-West Side Highway, e-Lower Manhattan, nge-October.
Kute kukhishwe sigwebo sekufa, bashushisi bekufanele bente bufakazi bekutsi Saipov "ngemacebo" wabulala labasiphohlongo futsi "ngemacebo" wabangela kulimala lokukhulu kwemtimba, ngekulandzela lesicelo sekukhishwa kwesigwebo sekufa, lesetfulwe e-Southern District yaseNew York.
Ngekusho kwemtsetfo, bobabili labantfu labashushiswa ngulaba lababili bebangabese bayabulawa.
Ngemuva kwemaviki lambalwa kubulawe lomuntfu, emajaji lamanyenti atfola Saipov anelicala lelimatima emacaleni la-22, lafaka ekhatsi emacala lasiphohlongo ekubulala ngekusebentisa lendlela yekucindzetela, laphindze abekwa bashushisi labatsandza kusebentisa emacala ebugebengu, kanye nemacala ekuhlasela ngekuhlukunyetwa kanye nekucedza konakalisa imoto.
Ngekusho kwemshushisi, lokuhlasela kwadzinga "kuhlelwa lokukhulu kanye nekulungiswa kwekucala", njengobe Saipov abekhombisa "bubi, budlova kanye nekungcola".
Kulesifungo, "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov uletse kulimala, ingoti nekulahlekelwa kumndeni nakubangani ba Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, na Alejandro Damian Pagnucco.
Bahlolwa bekuhambahamba kwebantfu labane.
Sekuphele iminyaka lelishumi kusukela sifundza saseNingizimu New York sacala licala lekugcina lekubulala.
Ngenyanga yeNyoni nga 2009, Khalid Barnes, lobekalahlwe ngelicala lekubulala bantfu lababili labebamphekele umutsi, wagcine atfole sigwebo sekufa.
Ecaleni lekugcina lapho kugwetjwa kufa khona enkantolo yaseNew York, bekungu-1953, lapho Julius na-Ethel Rosenberg, bantfu labashadile, batfolakala banelicala lekubulala ngekuhlanganyela ekuhlomiseni i-Soviet Union ngesikhatsi seMphi yeBumnene eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile.
Laba labashadile baseRosenberg babulawa ngesihlalo semandla agesi ngaJune 19, 1953.
Ngekusho kwemiculu yenkantolo, Saipov, wase-Uzbekistan, akazange akhombise kutivela buhlungu ngisho nangemuva kwetinyanga letimbalwa alandzela letentfo.
Ngesikhatsi aphendvulwa ngemaphoyisa, watsi ujabulile ngaloko lakwenta.
Saipov waphindze watjela tiphatsimandla kutsi kuhlaselwa kwakhe bekaphefumulelwe titfombe te-ISIS labetibukele ngelucingo lwakhe, njengobe bekashiwo.
Waphindze wacela kutsi kuphakanyiswe ifulegi ye-ISIS ekamelweni lakhe lasesibhedlela, kusho emaphoyisa.
Utivume angenacala kuto tonkhe tizatfu letingu-22 letibekwe embikwakhe.
David Patton, lomunye webameli bemphakatsi lophetse Saipov, uvakalise "kucabana lokusobala" ngesincumo semshushisi.
"Siphetsa ngekutsi sincumo sekufa kunekutsi semukele licala lelibekwe licala lekuphila ingunaphakadze ngaphandle kwekukhululwa, kutawuphindze kwente kube khona kuhlukunyetwa lokukhulu kulabo labatsintseka kulesentakalo", kusho Patton.
Kwatsi nakwendlula sikhatsi lesidze, licembu lelisekela Saipov lacela umshushisi kutsi angamgwebi.
