I-Park Byeong-seug, icaphuna idatha levela kuminisitari yekuhlanganisa bantfu baseNingizimu Afrika, itsi bekunebantfu labangu-1 127 labebashiya imimango yabo kulomnyaka lophelile - uma bacatsaniswa nalabangu-2 706 labashintja ngemnyaka wa 2011.
Inkhosi Park itsi kulawulwa kwemincele emkhatsini weNyakatfo neChina kanye nemitselo lephakeme lefunwa ngulabo labatsengisa ngetintfo letitsengwa ngaphandle kwebantfu, ngiko lokubaluleke kakhulu.
I-Pyongyang ayibekanga sobala.
Linyenti lebantfu baseNyakatfo labehlubukile bagcine sebaniketwe buve baseNingizimu Korea.
I-Seoul itsi bantfu labangetulu kwa-30 000 baseNyakatfo Korea bebahambile ngalokungekho emtsetfweni kusuka lapho kuphela khona imphi yaseKorea nga-1953.
Linyenti labo liyahamba lidzabule eChina, lelinebukhashane lobudze neNorth Korea futsi lelula kuyiwela kunaloko lokudzabuka endzaweni yekuphepha emkhatsini waletindzawo letimbili.
