Kuncintisana ngekuhweba kweMelika neChina kungaba njani yintfo lenhle kuBeijing
Kucala kwekuncintisana kutekuhwebelana emkhatsini weMelika neChina kuyachubeka, kantsi nanobe kusasele lokuncane kutsi kwentiwe, lokungavani emkhatsini walamave lamabili kungenteka kutsi kube lusito kuBeijing esikhatsini lesidze, ngekusho kwebachwephesha.
I-US President Donald Trump, wabhalisa umnyaka wakhe wekucala wekubukana netinkinga ngekukhokhisa intsela kuletinye tintfo letihamba phambili tase China kufaka ekhatsi ema-solar panels, intsimbi kanye ne-aluminium.
Kukhula lokukhulu kwaletintfo letitfolakalako kucale kuleli viki ngetinhlawulo letinsha letitsintsa tintfo letingu $200 billion (£150 billion), ngekusebenta kahle kwentela ihhafu yato tonkhe tintfo letingeniswa eUS ngeChina.
I-Beijing iphendvulele njalo, muva nje ikhokhe intsela lelisuka ku 5% kuya ku 10% emalini lengemadola latigidzi letingu 60 temikhicito yase Melika.
I-China seyivele icele kutsi ihlangane ne-US ngemalengiso, kantsi umnotfo wesibili lomkhulu emhlabeni awukashintji ngekushesha.
Kwenta iWashington kutsi ihambe kusho kwenta loko lefuna kutsi kwentiwe, kepha kulahla iMelika embikwebantfu kungaba yintfo lehlazisako ku Xi Jinping, longumengameli wase China.
Kodvwa, tati titsi uma iBeijing ingadlala kahle, kucindzeteleka lokukhulu kwekuncintisana kwemave aseMelika kungasita iChina esikhatsini lesidze lesidze ngekunciphisa kuncika kwelitiko lemnotfo.
"Liciniso lekutsi sincumo lesisheshako lesentiwa yi-Washington nobe yi-Beijing singabangela simo lesingaba yingoti kakhulu kunaloko lobekuvele kusetandleni tebabukeli", kusho Abigail Grace, losisebenti setenhlalo e-Asia e-Center for New American Security, lesinye setihlakaniphi.
Indvuna yetangaphandle itsi i-Syria 'ikulungele' kubuyiselwa kwalababalekile
I-Syria itsi ikulungele kubuyiselwa ngekutitsandzela kwalabo lababalekile, futsi icela lusito ekwakheni kabusha live layo lelahlelwa yimphi iminyaka lengetulu kwalelishumi nesikhombisa.
Sikhulumi sakhe lesinguSekela Lendvuna yeLitiko Letangaphandle, Walid al-Moualem, watsi simo sesihle kakhulu eveni lakhe.
"Lamuhla simo sisesimeni lesikahle kakhulu futsi sivikelekile ngenca yetintfo letenteke ekulweni nebuphekula", kwasho yena.
Hulumende uchubeka nekulungisa tindzawo letibhidlitwe tigebengu kute tibe nguloku lebetingiko.
Lesimo lesibekhona nyalo sibangwa kubuyela kwalababaleki eveni labebasuke kulo ngenca yekubhebhetseliswa kwebulandlululo kanye netincumo tetemnotfo letitsintsa imphilo yabo yalamuhla kanye nemphilo yabo.
Inhlangano yaMhlabuhlangene ilinganisela kutsi ngetulu kwa 5.5 wetigidzi tebantfu baseSiriya balahlekelwe live labo kusukela kwacala imphi nga-2011.
Bantfu labalinganiselwa ku-6 wetigidzi labahlala kulelo live badzinga lusito.
Al-Moualem utsi hulumende waseSyria utawutfola lusito lwekwakha kabusha live lakhe lelibhujisiwe.
Kodvwa wagcizelela kutsi angeke batemukele tibonelelo nobe lusito lolunemibandzela lwemave lasekela lokuvukela.
I-Europe icinisekise kutsi i-Ryder Cup iyancobeka eParis
Licembu laseYurophu lelake lancoba iRyder Cup lahlulwa licembu laseMelika ngemaphuzu lasemaphetselweni langu-16,5 na-10,5 e-Le Golf National ngaphandle kweParis, eFrance.
I-USA seyilahlekelwe tikhatsi letisitfupha letilandzelanako e-Europe futsi ayizange iphindze incobe i-Ryder Cup e-Europe kusukela nga-1993.
I-Europe yabuye yatfola lidzili layo ngesikhatsi indvuna yelicembu lase Denmark Thomas Bjorn atfola emaphuzu lalishumi nakune nesigamu ladzingekile kutsi abuke i-United States.
Phil Mickelson, lobekahamba libanga lelikhulu kulomdlalo, washaya i-tee yakhe emantini ngesikhatsi abamba ibhola ya-3 emgceni-16, avuma kuncotjwa ngu Francesco Molinari.
Umdlali we-golf wase-Italy Molinari uyawukhanya kulomdlalo, futsi nguye munye kubadlali labane labake batfola i5-0-0 seloku kwasungulwa lomdlalo nga-1979.
Umdlali waseMelika Jordan Spieth wehluliwe ngema-5 na-4 ngumdlali welicembu laseYurophu lophansi kakhulu, Thorbjorn Olesen waseDenmark.
Dustin Johnson, longumdlali lohamba phambili emhlabeni, wehlulwa kabili nakahlulwa ngu-Ian Poulter waseNgilandi, lobekangase adlale indzima yakhe yekugcina ku-Ryder Cup.
Sergio Garcia waseSpain, losaneminyaka lesiphohlongo adlala i-Ryder Cup, waba ngumdlali waseYurophu ngekuncoba ngalokuphelele nga-25.5 wemaphuzu labalulekile kulomncintiswano.
